\id 1CO
\h 1 Corintios
\toc1 Kart nech daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao beṉ'ka' nonḻilall' Jesucrístona' yell Coríntona'
\toc2 1 Corintios
\toc3 1 Co.
\mt1 Kart nech daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao beṉ'ka' nonḻilall' Jesucrístona' yell Coríntona'
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nad' Pablo nak' beṉ' gox wṉab Cristo Jesúza' kwenc̱he gak' postl c̱he' kon ka chaklall' Chioza'. Nad', len beṉ' bish'cho Sóstenezi, chwapnto' le' chiox.
\v 2 Chzej' le', le' chdop chllagle choe'la'ole Chioza' yell Coríntona', na' nakle lall' nee daa ba nonḻilall'le Jesucrístona'. Chioza' gox wṉabe' le' kwenc̱he gakle lall' nee len yog' beṉ'ka' choe'la'ogake' X̱ancho Jesucrístona' gattezə, ḻa' X̱ancho Jesucrístona' ḻekzka' nake' X̱angake'.
\v 3 X̱acho Chioza' len X̱ancho Jesucrístona' gaklenshgagake' le' na' wzoagake' le' mbalaz.
\p 
\v 4 Toshiizi cho'a Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken ka wen ba bene' c̱hele daa nonḻilall'le Cristo Jesúza'.
\v 5 Ḻa' daa ba naklene' txen, Chioza' chaklene' le' kwenc̱he chak gonle yog' diika' cheenile', ka choe'le xtilleena' na' leyi chajniilen.
\v 6 Na' ka', ba nakbia'cha dii ḻi ba wyajḻe'le xtill' Crístona' daa be'lennto' le'.
\v 7 Na' daa ba noṉ Chioza' le' daa chak gon to tole, ba chak chonle yog' daa cheenile gonle shlak chbezle yiyed X̱ancho Jesucrístona'.
\v 8 Na' gaklene' le' soac̱hec̱hle gonḻilall'lene' ax̱t llana' yiyede', kwenc̱he bibi xtoḻ'le gat' lawe'na'.
\v 9 Chios, beena' gox wṉab le' kwenc̱he nakle txen Xiiṉe' Jesucrístona', beena' nak X̱ancho, toshiizi chone' ka chc̱hebe'.
\p 
\v 10 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', chat'yoid' le' kon yeḻ' wṉabia' c̱he X̱ancho Jesucrístona', ḻi gak toz lao yog'ḻoḻte na' bi gonzə c̱he c̱hele, san toz ka ḻi se wṉeyi na' ḻi gon toz dill' lao bittezə dii gonle.
\v 11 Nia' ka', le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, ḻa' beṉ'ka' lle' lill Cloéna' ba wnagake' nad' ka chakdiḻ-len ljwell-le.
\v 12 Nia' ka', daa baḻ-le nale: “Nad' chon' txen Páblona'”, na' baḻ-le nale: “Nad' chon' txen Apóloza'.” Na' baḻ-le nale: “Nad' chon' txen Céfaza'.”\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Céfas: kan' le Pédrona' de dill' arameo, daa gok xtill' Jesúza'.\f* Na' zi baḻ-le nale: “Nad' nak' txen Crístona'.”
\v 13 ¿Achakile' Crístona' nake' c̱hop shoṉ kwenlə? ¿Awa chakile nadaan wit' ḻee yag cruza' ni c̱hele'? ¿Anti lia'na' bzetjgake' ka wchoale nisa'? Ṉezkzile bi nakan ka'.
\v 14 Chox̱ken Chioza' ni tole bi bchoa' nisa', ḻete Críspona' na' Gáyona',
\v 15 kwenc̱he kono iṉazə daa chone' nad' txenan wchoe' nis.
\v 16 Ḻekzka' bchoanis' beṉ'ka' lle' ḻoo yoo lill Estéfanaza', na' bi chjadinid' shi nochlə beṉ' yoblə bchoanis'.
\v 17 Ḻa' aga bseḻ' Crístona' nad' wchoa' beṉ' nis, san kwenc̱he c̱hix̱je'id' ḻegake' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'nan'. Na' ka chyix̱ji'an, bi chpaa dill'ka' cho'a kwenc̱he ki gaki beṉ' dill'ka' cho'a nakchan dii zak'chi aga ka daa wit Crístona' ḻee yag cruza'.
\p 
\v 18 Kat' no cho'e dill' c̱he daa wit Crístona' ḻee yag cruza', beṉ'ka' kwiayi' chakgakile' bizan chon chnan. San cho' yisla Chioza' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho, ṉezicho nakan dill' zakii dii nsa' yeḻ' wak c̱he'na'.
\v 19 Ḻa' Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan:
\q1 Yiṉitloa' yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' sin'ka'.
\q1 Na' gonllejid' beṉ'ka' chaki ḻe chajnii.
\p 
\v 20 ¿Bitgui gak gon beṉ' sin'ka' na' beṉ'ka' ḻe nsed ley c̱he Chioza', na' beṉ'ka' choe' dill' dii chaki beṉ' nakan dill' sin'? Ḻa' Chioza' ba bli'e bibi zakii yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni.
\v 21 Lo yeḻ' sin' c̱he'na', ba bene' kwenc̱he aga yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioki gaklenan ḻegake' gombia'gake' ḻe'. Ḻa' wyazlallee yisle' beṉ' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'gake' daa shajḻe'gake' xtill' Crístona' daa chyix̱je'i beṉ' ḻegake', ḻa'kzi chaki beṉ' bizan chon chnan.
\p 
\v 22 Ka nak beṉ' Israelka', ḻegake' chṉabgake' ile'gakile' yeḻ' wak kwenc̱he shajḻe'gake', na' beṉ' griegoka' chiyiljgake' daa chakgakile' nak yeḻ' sin'.
\v 23 San neto' chyix̱je'into' beṉ' daa wit Crístona' ḻee yag cruza', na' beṉ' Israelka' chakzbangakile' daa nanto' ka', na' beṉ'ka' bi nak beṉ' Israel chakgakile' biz dill' daa choe'nto'.
\v 24 San cho' ba gox wṉab Chioza' kwenc̱he nakcho lall' nee, ka neto' naknto' beṉ' Israel na' ka le' nakle beṉ' griego, ṉezicho Chioza' bli'e yeḻ' wak na' yeḻ' sin' c̱he'na' daa bseḻee Crístona' wite' ni c̱hecho.
\v 25 Na' dga ben Chioza' daa chaki beṉ' yell-lioni bizan chon chnan, ḻeyeṉ'lannan' nakchan to yeḻ' sin' xench aga ka bittezə yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni. Na' daa chaki beṉ' yell-lioni chli'n bi nap Chioza' yeḻ' wak, ḻeyeṉ'lannan' napchan yeḻ' wak aga ka bittezə yeḻ' wak dii nap beṉ' yell-lioni.
\v 26 Le' beṉ' bish', ḻi se wṉeyi ka nak daa gox wṉab Chioza' le' kwenc̱he nakle lall' nee ḻa'kzi aga zanle naple yeḻ' sin'na' de yell-lioni, ni aga zanle nakle beṉ' zakii, ni aga zanle goljle lo dia c̱he beṉ' zakii.
\v 27 Ḻa' Chioza' ba wleje' beṉ' bi nake' beṉ' sin' yell-lioni kwenc̱he wsi'e beṉ' sin'ka' yeḻ' zto', na' wleje' beṉ' bibi zakii yell-lioni kwenc̱he wsi'e beṉ'ka' zakii yeḻ' zto'.
\v 28 Chioza' ba wleje' beṉ' bibi zakii, na' beṉ' choni beṉ' ḻegake' nakzi, na' beṉ'ka' kono nakgake' yell-lioni, kwenc̱he chli'e bibi zakii yeḻ' zakii daa de yell-lioni.
\v 29 Na' ka', kono gak gon kwinin beṉ' choo beṉ' xen lawe'na'.
\v 30 Ḻa' kwinkzen' ba bene' ka gokcho Jesucrístona' txen. Na' daa ba nakcho Crístona' txen, Chioza' ba noṉe' cho' yeḻ' sin' c̱he'na', na' ba biyone' cho' beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao' lawe'na', na' ba bix̱is biyibe' yic̱hjlall'do'chona' na' ba bisell biḻee cho' lo ṉi'a na' dii mala'.
\v 31 Na' kon ka na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza': “Shi no cheeni wshalj wshon, chiyaḻ' wshalj wshone' c̱he yog' diika' ba ben X̱anchona' c̱he'.”
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', ka bidtix̱je'id' le' xtill' Chioza', aga bpaa dill'ka' be'len' le', ni bi bc̱hin' dill' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni.
\v 2 Kana' wzoa ladjlena', ben' to dii byen be'len' le' toz xtill' Jesucrístona' na' ka nak daa wite' ḻee yag cruza', na' bich bi dill' yoblə be'len' le'.
\v 3 Na' ka wzoalen' le', blleb' daa gokid' shi bi gak' wi'a xtill' Jesucrístona' ka chiyaḻ'.
\v 4 Na' ka bshaljlen' le' na' ka wdix̱je'id' le' xtill' Crístona', aga bi'a dill' dii chaki beṉ' nakan dill' sin' kwenc̱he kooyeḻaa le' shajḻe'le. San daa bi'a xtilleena' kon yeḻ' wak c̱he Espíritu c̱he Chiozan' wyajḻe'le.
\v 5 Ḻa' aga goklallaa shajḻe'le ni c̱he yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni, san daa yenile' dill'ka' nsa' yeḻ' wak c̱he Chiozan'.
\p 
\v 6 Dii ḻi de to yeḻ' sin' daa choe'lennto' beṉ'ka' ba nakcha nonḻilall'gake' Crístona'. Per bi nakan yeḻ' sin' c̱he yell-lioni, ni bi nakan yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ'ka' chṉabia'gake' lo yell-lioni, ḻa' wllin lla te c̱he beṉ'ka'.
\v 7 San chzajniinto' le' yeḻ' sin' c̱he Chioza' daa ngash' kani'teyi, daa wlo'e xṉezin kana' zi' wx̱e wsile' yell-lioni. Ḻa' kana'te wlo'e xṉezin yid Crístona' c̱hixje' xtoḻ'choka' kwenc̱he soacho mbalaz.
\v 8 Ni tlish' beṉ' wṉabia'ka' zoa yell-lioni bi wyajni'gakile' yeḻ' sin' c̱he Chioza', ḻa' sheḻ'ka' wyajni'gakile'n, bi betgake' X̱ancho Crístona' ḻee yag cruza', beena' ḻiizelozi nak beṉ' choo beṉ' xen.
\v 9 Per ka na cho'a xtill' Chioza':
\q1 Daa konoṉ' ile'i na' konoṉ' yeni, ni konoṉ' sa'lall' shi gakan,
\q1 ḻennan' wloo Chioza' xṉezin gone' c̱he beṉ'ka' chakgakile'ne'.
\m 
\v 10 Na' Chioza' ba bene' kwenc̱he Espíritu c̱he'na' ba bzajniile' cho' c̱heyi diika'. Na' Espíritu c̱he'na' ṉez nḻe'ile' yog'ḻoḻ, na' chajniile' kwasḻoḻ yog' daa nak c̱he Chioza'.
\p 
\v 11 Ḻa' cho' beṉ' yell-lio shinchozə ṉezicho dii yoo ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do' kwincho, na' bi ṉezicho bi yoo ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do' beṉ' yoblə. Ka'kzan, toz Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ṉez nḻe'ile' daa ngoo Chioza' xṉezin.
\v 12 Na' cho' aga yeḻ' sin' daa de yell-lionin chc̱hincho, san Chioza' ba beṉe' cho' Espíritu c̱he'na' kwenc̱he chajniicho ka nak dii wenna' daa ba noṉe' cho'.
\v 13 Na' neto', kat' choe'nto' xtill' Crístona', aga chc̱hinnto' yeḻ' sin'na' de yell-lionizə, san chzajniinto' diika' chzajnii Espíritu c̱he Chioza' neto', na' chc̱hinnto' dill' daa chzajniile' neto'.
\p 
\v 14 Na' beena' bi yoo Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'ena', bi chajḻi'e dill' daa chzajnii Espíritu c̱he Chioza', daa chakile' bizan chon chnan. Na' bi chajniile'n daa chyalljin gaklen Espírituna'ne' kwenc̱he shajniile'n.
\v 15 San beena' yoo Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'ena' chajniile' c̱he bittezə daa cheeni Chioza' iṉezile', na' kono gak bi iṉa c̱he'.
\v 16 Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Ni to kono ṉezi daa cheeni X̱ancho Chioza' gone', na' ni to kono gak wzajniile'ne' nakan chiyaḻ' gone'.” San cho' ba yoo Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'choni, ba chajniicho daa cheeni Crístona' gone'.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', bi gok we'len' le' ka dill'ka' choe'len' beṉ'ka' ba nakcha lo xṉez Chioza', daa ni chonle ka nazan c̱hele, na' ni nakle ka bi'do' daa biṉ' shajni'yeṉ'ile c̱he Crístona'.
\v 2 Na' ka chon beṉ' kon bdo' cheeṉna' cho'eb' nillaa daa biṉ' gak gaob' yeḻ' wawa', kan' ben' c̱hele, bi be'len' le' dill' dii nak lallj, ḻa' biṉ' gak shajniilen. Na' ni ṉaa biṉ' shajni'kzilen.
\v 3 Nia' ka', daa ni chonle daa nazan c̱hele. Daa chakxe'i ljwell-le, na' chakdiḻ-len ljwell-le, chli'n ni chonle ka nazan c̱hele na' chonle ka beṉ' bi nombia' Chioza'.
\v 4 Daa na baḻ-le: “Nad' nak' txen Páblona'”, na' zi baḻ-le nale: “Nad' nak' txen Apóloza'”, ¿abi chakbe'ile ka beṉ' bi nombia' Chiozan' chonle?
\p 
\v 5 ¿No nak Apóloza'? Na' ¿no nak' nad'? Zeelochoz naknto' wen llin c̱he X̱ancho Crístona', na' ḻe' bene' ka benḻilall'lene' ka be'lennto' le' xtilleena'. To to neto' bennto' kon ka wlo'e xṉezin gonnto'.
\v 6 Nad' nak' ka beena' goz daa wdis' xtill' Crístona' ladjlena', na' Apóloza' nake' ka beena' wdil, daa bli' bsedchile' le'. Per Chioza' bene' ka wyajḻe'le daa bli' bsedinto' le'.
\v 7 Na' aga no nak beena' chaz ni beena' chyil, ḻa' toz Chiozan' chone' ka chgol daa ba byaz.
\v 8 Toz ka zak' beena' chaz na' beena' chyil. Na' Chioza' gone' kwenc̱he to toe' si'e banez kon ka nak llinna' daa bene'.
\v 9 Neto' naknto' txen chonnto' xshin Chioza' ladjlena', na' naknto' ka beṉ' goz gooṉ c̱he', na' le' nakle ka yell-lio c̱he' gana' chonnto' llinna'. Na' ḻekzka' nakle ka to yoo c̱he' dii chonnto'.
\p 
\v 10 Chioza' ba goklene' nad' chon' xshine'na' ladjlena', na' daa ben' ladjlena' nakan ka beṉ' wlek to len yoo, na' beṉ' yoblə chḻise' zeeka'. Na' to to wen llin chiyaḻ' wsakee shi chone' llinna' ka chiyaḻ' gakan.
\v 11 Na' kono gak wx̱e sto len yoblin, ḻa' Jesucrístonan' zaklebile' len yoona' ba chi'.
\v 12 Na' lo len yooni, zoa beṉ' wx̱eile'n or wa plat, wa yaj dii zakii, na' zoa beṉ' wx̱eile'n yagla', wa yeje, wa yix.
\v 13 Na' llinna' daa gon to toe' wli'lawin shi nakan dii zakii. Ḻa' kat' illin lla gon Chioza' yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni, yi' c̱he'na' wzeyan daa bi zakii, na' gakbia' nak nak llinna' ben to toe'.
\v 14 Na' shi no ben to dii bi shey, na' si'e banez c̱he xshine'na'.
\v 15 Per shi daa bene' sheyan, na' bibi banez si'e c̱heyin. Na' kayaadia yile' bi kwiayee lo yi'na'.
\p 
\v 16 ¿Abi chakbe'ile nan le' chdop chllagle choe'la'ole Crístona' nakle ka lill xḻatj Chioza', na' Espíritu c̱he'na' zoe' ladjlena'?
\v 17 Na' shi no wlliayi' lill xḻatje'na', Chioza' wlliayee beena' gon ka', na' len' nakle ka lill xḻatj Chioza' daa nakle lall' nee.
\p 
\v 18 Bi siye' kwinle. Shi nole chakile nakle beṉ' sin' daa naple yeḻ' sin' c̱he yell-lioni, chiyaḻ' yiyakle ka to beṉ' bibi chajnii lao beṉ' yell-lioni kwenc̱he Chioza' goṉe' le' dowalj yeḻ' sin'na'.
\v 19 Ḻa' yeḻ' sin' c̱he beṉ' yell-lioni aga bi zakaan lao Chioza'. Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Chioza' chone' kwenc̱he beṉ' sin'ka' chakc̱hix̱gakile' lo yeḻ' sin' c̱he'ka'.”
\v 20 Na' ḻekzka' nan: “X̱ancho Chioza' nombi'e yog'ḻoḻ daa chza'lall' beṉ' yell-lioni, na' ṉezile' nakan dii bibi zakii.”
\v 21 Daan, ni tole bi chiyaḻ' gakle beṉ' cha'sib daa shi non nakle txen, ḻa' yog' beṉ' na' yog' dii de nakan c̱hele kwenc̱he si'le banez c̱heyin:
\v 22 ḻaa nad' Pablo, ḻaa Apóloza', ḻaa Céfaza', ḻaa yell-lioni, ḻaa yeḻ' mbanna', ḻaa yeḻ' wita', ḻaa daa chak ṉaa, ḻaa daa zi' gak. Yog'nto' len yog' diika' nakgakan c̱hele kwenc̱he si'le banez c̱heyin.
\v 23 Na' le' nakle lall' na' Crístona', na' Crístona' nake' lall' na' Chioza'.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Chiyaḻ' gakbe'ile neto' naknto' wen llin c̱he Crístona', na' nak lo na'nto' chzajniinto' beṉ' daa kono wṉezi daa wloo Chioza' xṉezin.
\v 2 Na' chonan byen gonnto' kon ka ba none' lall' na'nto' gonnto'.
\v 3 Na' aga bitek wṉeyi zia' shi le' wa ḻaa x̱oṉj beṉ' chi'e nad' kwent wṉeyi shi chak gon' xshin Chioza' ka chiyaḻ'. Ni nad' biga chbi'a kwent wṉeyi c̱he kwin' shi chon' ka chiyaḻ'.
\v 4 Na' ḻa'kzi bibi de dii chao chdian nad', aga ni c̱he ka' bibi doḻ' c̱ha' de. Toz X̱ancho Crístona' ṉez nḻe'ile' shi chon' ka chiyaḻ' gon'.
\v 5 Na' daan, bi chiyaḻ' sele kwent wṉeyi beṉ', san ḻi kwez ax̱t kat'ka' yila' X̱ancho Crístona' na' wli'e lawi daa ngash' ṉaa na' daa yoo ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do' yog' beṉ'. Kana'chan gon Chioza' ka sho'cho balaaṉ shi bencho ka cheenile'.
\p 
\v 6 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', choe'len' le' dill'ki kwenc̱he gak wen c̱hele, na' cho'a dill' c̱he kwin' len xtill' Apóloza' kwenc̱he iṉezile ka chonnto' na' wsedle bi tele lawi daa na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza'. Na'ch bi gakle beṉ' cha'sib na' soazle c̱he baḻ beṉ' na' gonzile zi baḻe' nakzi.
\v 7 ¿Achakile nakchle beṉ' zak'chi aga ka beṉ' yoblə? Ḻa' Chioza' beṉe' diika' ba naple. Na' daa beṉ Chioza'gakan, ¿berac̱he chshalj chshonzle c̱heyin ka iṉacho tobia'lozlen bllelilen?
\p 
\v 8 Le' chakile bich bi chyalljile. Chakile ba nakle ka beṉ' wni'a daa noṉ Chioza' diika' gak gon to tole. Chakile ba chṉabia'lenle Crístona' na' bich chyalljile neto'. Ḻe mba sheḻ' dii ḻi ba chṉabia'le, kwenc̱he len neto' iṉabia'lennto' le', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 9 Chakid' Chioza' ba none' kwenc̱he neto' postl naknto' ka beṉ' ḻiizelozi bibi zakii, na' ka beṉ' nchogbia' guet. Na' yog'te beṉ' yell-lioki na' len anjlka' chibangakile' chwiagake' ka chak c̱hento'.
\v 10 Beṉ' zan chakgakile' naknto' beṉ' bi nteyi daa chonnto' xshin Crístona', san le', chon kwinle ka beṉ' ḻe chajnii daa nonḻilall'le Crístona'. Neto' chakbe'into' bibi chak gonnto', san le' chakile chak gonle bittezə. Chle'shii beṉ' le', san neto', chle'zbani beṉ' neto'.
\v 11 Ax̱t ṉaanlla zoa kat' chbiḻ chdonnto', chyallj xalaannto', chsak'zi' beṉ' neto', na' aga bi lill xḻatjnto' de.
\v 12 Na' chisto yic̱hj chisto lall'nto' chonnto' llin kon ṉi'a na'nto'ki kwenc̱he gat' dii yeej gaonto'. Zoa beṉ' chyishjgake' bia' blag' c̱hento', na' neto' chṉablnto' gaklen Chioza' ḻegake'. Chc̱hi chsak'gake' neto' na' chzo chzakinto' daa chongakile' neto'.
\v 13 Chiya dii nagake' c̱hento', na' neto' choe'lento' ḻegake' dill' xochi. Na' chongakile' neto' ka beṉ' zeelo bibi zakii, ka to dii ba wchooṉ beṉ'. Ax̱t ṉaanlla ni chongakile' neto' ka'.
\p 
\v 14 Aga chzej' dga kwenc̱he wsi'a le' yeḻ' zto', san kwenc̱he wzajniid' le', daa chakid' le' ka xiiṉ'.
\v 15 Na' ḻa'kzi zoa shi mil beṉ' wzajniile' le' c̱he Crístona', toz beena' nak ka x̱alen zoa. Ḻa' nadaan nak' ka x̱ale daa wlo'a le' lo xṉez Cristo Jesúza' ka be'len' le' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'na'.
\v 16 Daan chat'yoid' le', ḻi gon ka chon'.
\p 
\v 17 Na' daan, ba bseḻaa Timotewa' gana' zoale. Chakidee ka dowalj xiiṉ' na' chone' xshin Crístona' ka chiyaḻ' gone'. Ḻe' yisee lall'le ka nsa' c̱ha' lo xṉez Crístona', na' ka chzajniid' beṉ'ka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona' doxen gana' chda'.
\v 18 Baḻ-le ba chep cha'lall'le daa chakile' bich yidwia' le'.
\v 19 Per shi X̱anchona' wi'e latj, yob yidwia' le' na' ile'id' shi beṉ'ka' chep cha'lall' dii ḻi chak gongake' ka nagake' wa shi chshaljzgaken'.
\v 20 Aga de dill'zan iṉacho ba chṉabia' Chioza' cho', san daa gapcho yeḻ' wak c̱he'nan' na'chan gak goncho ka cheenile'.
\v 21 ¿Nakra cheenile gon' kat' yidwia' le'? ¿Acheenile gonid' le' zṉia?, anti ¿we'len' le' dill' xochi daa ḻe chakid' le'?
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Ba benid' dill' nagake' nan len to beṉ' ladjlena' zoalene' xṉa'zi'ena' ka xoole'. Daa chon beena' nakan to dii zban inlleb; ni beṉ'ka' bi nombia' Chioza' bi chongake' ka'.
\v 2 Na' ḻa'kzi chak ka' ladjlena', ni chep cha'lall'zle daa chakile ba chonle ka cheeni Chioza'. Chiyaḻ'lə gakyeshilen na' yibejle beena' chon ka'.
\v 3 Ḻa'kzi ṉaa bi zoa' gana' zoale, ḻe chi' yic̱hj' ka nsa' c̱hele. Na' kon ḻi gaktezi na'kzan zoalen' le', na' ḻi gon ka ba bc̱hogloa' gak c̱he beena' ben ka'.
\v 4 Na' kat' ndi'a nllagle choe'la'ole X̱ancho Jesúza', ḻi gaktezi na'kzan zoa' ladjlena', na' daa zoalen yeḻ' wak c̱he X̱ancho Jesúza' le',
\v 5 ḻi yibej beena' na' ḻi gone' lall' na' Satanáza' kwenc̱he shi yiyakbe'ile' na' yiyaj yilenile' na' yile' lo yeḻ' zi'na' daa za' llana' wc̱hoglo X̱anchona' c̱he beṉ'.
\p 
\v 6 Bi nakan wen chep cha'lall'le. Ba ṉezkzile dillaa de nan: “Lat'z levadúrana' chisgolan doxen kwa c̱he yetxtila'.”
\v 7 Dii mal daa ben beena' ladjlena' nakan ka levadúrana'. Na' ka neto' beṉ' Israel bi choe'nto' latj yigaaṉ ni lat' levadúrana' ḻoo yoo lillnto' kat' chaḻ' lṉi Paskwa', ka'kzə le' chiyaḻ' kwejle beena' chon zban ladjlena' kwenc̱he gakle ka kwa kob daa bi nc̱hix̱ levadúrana', kon ka ba nakkzle. Ḻa' Crístona', beena' zaklebi xil'do'na' chitgake' Paskwa', ba wite' ni c̱hecho.
\v 8 Na' ka chon beṉ'ka' chon lṉi Paskwa' chbejgake' yog'ḻoḻ daa nc̱hix̱ levadúrana', ka'kzə cho' chiyaḻ' soa kwezcho bich goncho saaxyana' na' bi dii mal daa bencho kani'yi, san soacho do yic̱hj do lall'cho shajlencho daa nak dii ḻi.
\p 
\v 9 Ba bzejkz' le' to shii wnia' le' bi gonlenle txen beṉ'ka' chdalen ljwellin.
\v 10 Daa wnia' bi chiyaḻ' gonle txen beṉ'ka' chdalen ljwellgake', wa chzelall'gake' gat' kwe'gakile' dii de yell-lioni, wa chbangake', wa choe'la'ogake' no yaj yag, aga c̱he beṉ'ka' bi nombia' Chiozan' nia' ka', ḻa' sheḻ' bi gak ḻencho ladje'ka' chiyaḻ' ichejtekzcho lo yell-lioni, sheḻ'ka'.
\v 11 San daa wnia' ka' zejin bi gak ḻencho nottezə beṉ' ne' nake' cho' txen nonḻilall'cho Crístona' na' chdalene' xiiṉ xool beṉ', wa chzelallile' gat' kwe'ile' dii de yell-lioni, wa choe'la'owe' no yaj yag, wa chbell chṉie' c̱he beṉ', wa nake' weezo, wa nake' beṉ' wban. Yog' beṉ'ka' chon ka', ni bi yeej gaolenle ḻegake'.
\v 12 Bi nak lall' na'cho kwe'cho kwent wṉeyi beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall' Crístona'. San beṉ'ka' nakcho txen nonḻilall'cho Crístona', ḻegaken' chiyaḻ' kwe'cho kwent wṉeyi.
\v 13 Chioza' yizi'e kwent beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall' Crístona'. Na' le', ḻi yibej beena' chon dii mala' ladjlena'.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Kat' tole de to dii zed c̱hele kon sto beena' nakle txen nonḻilall'le Crístona', bi chiyaḻ' shajle lao beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall' Crístona' kwenc̱he gongake' yeḻ' josc̱his c̱helena', san ḻi shaj lao beṉ'ka' nak lall' na' Chioza' kwenc̱he gongake' yeḻ' josc̱his c̱helena'.
\v 2 ¿Abi ṉezile wllin lla le' nakle lall' na' Chioza' gonle yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he beṉ' yell-lioki? Na' shi len' gonle yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he'ka', ḻekzka' wak gonle yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he bizə diido'ka' chak ṉaa.
\v 3 ¿Abi ṉezile ax̱t anjlka' goncho yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he'ka'? Na' shi goncho yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he anjlka', ¿abi gak goncho yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he diiki chak ṉaa zoacho yell-lioni?
\v 4 Na' shi le' chakdiḻ-len ljwell-le ni c̱he biz diika' chak c̱hele, ¿berac̱he chajzle lao josc̱hiska' beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall'gake' Crístona', beṉ'ka' bibi zakii ladjlena'?
\v 5 Nia' le' ka' kwenc̱he yido'latile. ¿Aniga tlish'le bi nteyi kwenc̱he gak gonle yeḻ' josc̱his c̱he beṉ'ka' nonḻilall'lenle Crístona'?
\v 6 Latjin dii gonlen ladjle na'z, ba zejzle zjtaole xya c̱he ljwell-le lao josc̱hiska' bi nonḻilall' Crístona'.
\p 
\v 7 Na' daa chao xya c̱he ljwell-le chli'n bi nsa' c̱hele wen. ¿Bic̱he ki chonxenlall'le yog' dii choni beṉ' le', wa ki chonle ka'z kat' no chzi' chban bi de c̱hele?
\v 8 Per le'lə, lwaa dii gonle ka', dii zan dii choni ljwell-le na' chizi' chibantezle c̱he ljwell-le.
\p 
\v 9 ¿Abi ṉezile beṉ'ka' bi chon wen aga willingake' gana' zoa Chioza' chṉabi'e? Bi siye'z kwinle, ḻa' ka nak beṉ'ka' chdalen ljwellin, beṉ'ka' choe'la'o yaj yagka', beṉ'ka' bi chon banez xoolin wa noolka' bi chon banez beṉ' c̱heyin, beṉ' xejka',
\v 10 beṉ' wbanka', beṉ'ka' chzelallii gat' kwe'gakile' daa de yell-lioni, beṉ' weezoka', beṉ'ka' chbell chṉe c̱he beṉ', wa beṉ'ka' chyiljlall' naklə si' kwangake' bi de c̱he beṉ', ni to beṉ'ka' chon diiki bi yillingake' gana' zoa Chioza' chṉabi'e.
\v 11 Na' baḻ-le gokle ka beṉ' malki kana'. Per ṉaa Chioza' ba bix̱is biyibe' le', ba none' le' yell c̱he', na' ba biyone' le' beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao' lawe'na' daa ba nonḻilall'le X̱ancho Jesucrístona' na' daa chon Espíritu c̱he'na' llin lo yeḻ' mban c̱helena'.
\p 
\v 12 Dill' de, nan: “De latj goncho bittezə.” Ḻikzan, per aga yog' daa goncho nakan wen. Na' ḻa'kzi de latj goncho bittezə, bi chiyaḻ' we'cho latj iṉabia'n cho'.
\v 13 Ṉezicho yeḻ' wawa' nakan c̱he ḻeechoni, na' ḻeechoni none'n kwenc̱he shoon yeḻ' wawa'. Per Chioza' gone' ka te c̱he c̱hopte diiki. Na' kwerp c̱hechoni aga none'n kwenc̱he nottez gat'lencho, san kwenc̱he goncho daa cheeni X̱ancho Crístona', na' X̱anchona' nak lall' nee kwerp c̱hechoni.
\v 14 Na' ka bisban Chioza' X̱ancho Jesucrístona' ladj beṉ' wetka' kon yeḻ' wak c̱he'na', ka'kzan yisbane' cho' ladj beṉ' wetka'.
\p 
\v 15 Ṉezile yog'cho nonḻilall'cho Crístona' chzaklebicho tkwen wej kwerp c̱he'na'. Na' biga chiyaḻ' wc̱hincho kwerp c̱hechoki nak ka tkwen wej kwerp c̱he Crístona' kwenc̱he gat'lencho noolə wdana'.
\v 16 ¿Abi ṉezile nottezə beṉ' gat'lene' to noolə wda, chake'ne' toz? Ḻa' Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Beṉ'ka' c̱hop gakgake' toz kwerp.”
\v 17 Per beena' chon kwine' lall' na' X̱ancho Crístona', chake'ne' toz daa yoo Espíritu c̱he'na' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'ena'.
\p 
\v 18 Bi wc̱hinle kwerp c̱helena' gat'lenzle nottez beṉ', ḻi ikwas lao dii mala' nak ka'. Ḻa' ḻennan' chx̱iṉj chḻenchan kwerp c̱hechona' aga ka bichlə dii mal yoblə. Beena' gon to dii mal yoblə, aga bi nonan c̱he kwerp c̱he'na', san daa chon beena' chc̱hin kwerp c̱he'na' chat'lene' nottez, chx̱iṉj chḻenan do ka nake'.
\v 19 ¿Abi ṉezile kwerp c̱hechoni nakan lill xḻatj Espíritu Sántona', beena' bzoa Chioza' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'choni? Na' bi gak goncho daa nazan c̱hecho;
\v 20 ḻa' Crístona' ba biya'o bizi'e cho' daa blalj xc̱hene'na' na' wite' ni c̱hecho kwenc̱he nakcho lall' na' Chioza'. Daan yog' daa gonlen kwerp c̱hechoni chiyaḻ' gonchon ka sho' Chioza' balaaṉ.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Ka nak diika' wṉabile nad' ka bzejle nad', nad' nia' nakan wen shi bi ikaa c̱he beṉ' byona'.
\v 2 Per daa zoale dii nxoll gat'lenle nottez ka chon beṉ' yell-lioni, daan to to beṉ' byo chiyaḻ' soa nool c̱he', na' ḻekzka' to to noolə chiyaḻ' soa beṉ' c̱he'.
\v 3 Na' beṉ'ka' nshagna', ka beṉ' byo ka nool, bi chiyaḻ' wlloni ljwellgake' kwerp c̱he'ka'.
\v 4 Ḻa' noola' aga nak kwerp c̱he'na' c̱he toze', san nakan len c̱he beṉ' c̱he'na'. Na' ka'kzə beṉ' c̱he'na' bi nak kwerp c̱he'na' c̱he toze', san nakan len c̱he xoole'na'.
\v 5 Na' daan bi wlloni ljwell-le kwerp c̱heleka', per shi c̱hoptele ba be'le dill' bi gat'len ljwell-le to tiemp kwenc̱he we'ḻwill-le Chioza', aga bi nonan. Na' tena' chiyaḻ' yiyell ljwell-le dii yoblə kwenc̱he bi soale dii nxoll gon dii x̱iwaa le' gan na' we'le cho'a xbayi beli chenna' talenle beṉ' yoblə.
\p 
\v 6 Nia' le' ka' kwenc̱he iṉezile wak wshagna' beṉ' byona' na' noola', per bi chonan byen shi bi cheengakile'.
\v 7 Nad' chakid' nakan wen sheḻ'ka' yog' beṉ' byo soe' toze' ka zoa' nad', per wde wdeli nak daa noṉ Chioza' gon to tocho.
\p 
\v 8 Na' le' biṉ' wshagna'le, na' ḻekzka' le' ba wit beṉ' c̱heleka', nia' le' naklan wen soa tozle, ka zoa' nad'.
\v 9 Per shi bi yizoilen, wenchoklə ikaa c̱hele kwenc̱he bi sho' shejlall'le selall'le nool wa beṉ' byo daa chonan lallj iṉabia' kwinle.
\p 
\v 10 Na' le' nshagna'le, nia' le' kon ka non X̱ancho Crístona' mandad gonle, aga nakan dii nia' nad': Noola' bi chiyaḻ' yiḻee beṉ' c̱he'na'.
\v 11 Na' shi noola' yiḻee beṉ' c̱he'na', bi chiyaḻ' yikee beṉ' yoblə, san wenlan yiyoe'xene' beṉ' c̱he'na' na' yikeene' dii yoblə. Na' ka'kzə beṉ' byona' bi chiyaḻ' yiḻee xoole'na'.
\p 
\v 12 Ka le' nshagna'le na' bi nonḻilall'le Crístona' c̱hoptele, nia' le' dga, per bi nakan daa nllia X̱anchona' bia' gonle: shi to beṉ' byo nshagna'lene' to noolə bi nonḻilall' Crístona', na' noola' none' lez gax̱'she'lene'ne', bi chiyaḻ' yiḻaa beṉ' c̱he'na' ḻe'.
\v 13 Na' shi to noolə nshagna'lene' to beṉ' byo bi nonḻilall' Crístona', na' beṉ' c̱he'na' none' lez gax̱'she'lene'ne', bi chiyaḻ' yiḻaa xoole'na' ḻe'.
\v 14 Beṉ' byona', beena' bi nonḻilallee Crístona' shi nshagnee to noolə beṉ' ba nonḻilalleene', Chioza' chle'shiile'ne' ni c̱he nool c̱he'na'. Na' noola', beena' bi nonḻilallee Crístona', shi nshagnee to beṉ' byo beṉ' ba nonḻilalleene', Chioza' chle'shiilene' ni c̱he beṉ' c̱he'na'. Sheḻ' bi nakan ka', bi chle'shii Chioza' xiiṉe'ka', sheḻ'ka'. San daa nonḻilall' togake' Crístona', Chioza' chle'shiile' xiiṉe'ka'.
\v 15 Per shi xoolo'na' wa beṉ' c̱ho'na', beena' bi nonḻilallee Crístona', bich cheenile' soalene' li', be' latj yiyaje'. Bi chonan byen soayaadialenzo'ne', ḻa' Chioza' ba gox wṉabe' cho' kwenc̱he soacho mbalaz.
\v 16 Na' li' nonḻilalloo Crístona', bi ṉezilo' shi wak gono' kwenc̱he beṉ' c̱ho'na' wa xoolo'na' gonḻilallee Crístona' na' yile' bi kwiayi'e.
\p 
\v 17 To tocho, ka beṉ' nshagna' ka beṉ' zoa toze', chiyaḻ' soacho kon ka non X̱anchona' c̱hecho ka gox wṉab Chioza' cho'. Ka'kzə chon' byen gon yog' kwen beṉ'ka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona'.
\v 18 Shi nole yoole seṉ daa le circuncisión ka gox wṉab Chioza' le', bi gonle ka yinit seṉna'. Na' shi bi yoole seṉna' ka gox wṉab Chioza' le', bi koo kwinle seṉ.
\v 19 Aga bi nonan shi yoocho seṉna' wa shi bi yoochon, san daa llialote goncho ka nllia' Chioza' bia'.
\v 20 To tocho chiyaḻ' soacho kon ka nakcho ka gox wṉab Chioza' cho'.
\v 21 Shi ba nzi' beṉ' li' kwenc̱he gono' xshine'na' ka gox wṉab Chioza' li', bibi gakilo'. Per shi sho'ilo' xṉezin yisane' li', ben to dii byen.
\v 22 Ḻa' beena' ndoo chon xshin beṉ' ka gox wṉab Chioza'ne', Crístona' ba bisell biḻeene' lao dii mala'. Na' beena' chon xshinkze' ka gox wṉab Chioza' ḻe', ba nak Crístona' X̱ane' daa ba biya'o bizi'ene' lao dii mala'.
\v 23 Daa wit Crístona' biya'o bizi'e cho' lo ṉi'a na' dii mala'. Daan chiyaḻ' wzenagchcho c̱he' aga ka c̱he nottez beṉ'.
\v 24 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', kon ka zoacho ka gox wṉab Chioza' cho', ka'kzan soa kwezcho lawe'na'.
\p 
\v 25 Na' ka le' ni zoale tozle, bi nllia X̱ancho Crístona' bia' nak gonle, per nad' iṉia' ka chakid' chiyaḻ' gonle. Na' daa ba biyesh'lallii X̱anchona' nad', zak'kzi xtillaana' wzenaglen.
\v 26 Nad' chakid' nakan wen soale kon ka zoale ṉaa, ḻa' llaki zoacho nakgakan dii lallj.
\v 27 Shi zoa nool c̱hele bi yiḻaalene'. Na' shi kono nool c̱hele zoa, bi gonle byen ikaa c̱hele.
\v 28 Shi wshagna'le, bi nakan mal; na' shi to nool wew' wshagna'b' ḻekzka' aga bi mal nakan. Per dii zan dii zed chen chle'i beṉ'ka' nshagna', na' chaklallaa bi gak c̱hele ka'.
\p 
\v 29 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', cheenid' iṉia' le' dga: Zi' lat'chga latj c̱hecho de. Daan, le' nshagna'le, bi we'le latj wsej wllon nool c̱helena' gonle ka cheeni Chioza'.
\v 30 Na' shi nole zoale nyesh' bi we'le latj wsej wllonan gonle ka cheeni Chioza'. Na' shi nole zoale mbalaz, bi we'le latj wsej wllonan gonle ka cheeni Chioza'. Na' shi nole cha'o chzi'le bittezə, bi we'le latj wsej wllonan gonle ka cheeni Chioza'.
\v 31 Na' shi nole chzi'le banez dii de yell-lioni, bi we'le latj wsej wllonan gonle ka cheeni Chioza'; ḻa' yell-lioni dga nombia'cho nakan dii te c̱heyin.
\p 
\v 32 Nad' chaklallaa bibi sele wṉeyi c̱heyin, sheḻ'ka'. Ḻa' beṉ' byona' bi nshagna' chzeche' wṉeyi daa nak c̱he X̱anchona' kwenc̱he gone' ka yiyoolallee.
\v 33 San beena' nshagna' chzeche' wṉeyi c̱heyi daa de yell-lioni na' nak gone' kwenc̱he yiyoolallii nool c̱he'na' daa chone',
\v 34 na' c̱hoplə nak diika' chzie' wṉeyi c̱heyin. Na' nool tona' na' ka'kzə nool wewaa zechgake' wṉeyi c̱he daa nak c̱he X̱anchona', na' do ka nakgake' chon kwingake' lall' nee kwenc̱he gongake' daa cheenile'. San noola' nshagna' chzeche' wṉeyi c̱heyi daa de yell-lioni na' nak gone' kwenc̱he yiyoolallii beṉ' c̱he'na' daa chone'.
\p 
\v 35 Nia' le' ka' aga daa cheenid' wsej wllon' bi gonle, san daa cheenid' gaklen' le' gonle ka chiyaḻi, kwenc̱he bibi wllonan gon kwinle lall' na' X̱ancho Crístona' do ka nakle na' gonle ka cheenile'.
\p 
\v 36 Shi to bi' wew' ba nakan ikaab' to nool wew' bi' ba nzag'b', na' chakib' wenan ikaab' ḻeb' daa ba goḻb', wshagna'chb', aga bi mal chom'.
\v 37 Per shi zoa bi' wew' chakib' bi chonan byen ikaab' noolə na' wzoib' beli chen c̱hebaa kwenc̱he bi wx̱iṉj wḻem', wenan gom' bi wshagna'b'.
\v 38 Na' bi'na' wshagna' wenkzan chom', per bi'na' bi wshagna'b' chontechb' wen.
\p 
\v 39 Na' noola' nshagna', chonan byen soalene' toz beṉ' c̱he'na',shlak mbane'; per shi guet beṉ' c̱he'na', wak yikee beṉ' yoblə, kon shi nake' beṉ' nonḻilall' X̱ancho Crístona'.
\v 40 Per nad' chakid' wzoache' mbalazch shi bich yikaa c̱he'. Na' dga ba wnia', chakid' Espíritu c̱he Chioza' yoo ḻoo yic̱hjlall'dawa'nin na ka'.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Na' ka nak c̱he yeḻ' wawa' daa chllia beṉ' lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka', yog'cho ṉezicho c̱heyi dga. Per nxoll gakcho beṉ' cha'sib daa chakicho ḻe ṉezicho. San shi napcho yeḻ' chakina', wzecho wṉeyi gaklen ljwellcho gakchachcho.
\v 2 Na' beena' chaki ḻe ṉezile', chiyaḻ' gakbe'ile' bi ṉezile' ka chiyaḻ'.
\v 3 Per beena' ḻe chakile' Chioza', Chioza' nombi'ene'.
\p 
\v 4 Na' ka nak yeḻ' wawa' daa chllia beṉ' lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka', ṉezicho lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka' bibi zak'gakan, san toz Chiozan' zoa.
\v 5 Dii ḻi de dii zan daa na beṉ' nakgakan chios c̱hegake'. Per ḻa'kzi nagake' zoa chios c̱hegake' na' x̱angake' yabana' wa lo yell-lioni,
\v 6 cho' ṉezicho toz Chiozan' zoa, beena' nak X̱acho. Ḻen' bx̱e bsil yog'ḻoḻte dii de, na' zoacho kwenc̱he we'la'ochone'. Na' ḻekzka' zoa toz beena' nak X̱ancho, na' ḻen' Jesucrístona', beena' bx̱e bsile' yog'ḻoḻte dii de, na' ni c̱hen' mbancho.
\p 
\v 7 Per aga yog' beṉ' ṉezgakile' dga. Baḻ beṉ' wyoologake' be'la'ogake' lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka', na' kat' cheej chaogake' yeḻ' wawa' daa ba bllia beṉ' lawinka' chakgakile' txenan chonlengake'n. Na' daa biṉ' gakbe'gakile' bibi zakii diika', chakgakile' malan' chongake' kat' cheej chaogake' yeḻ' wawa'.
\v 8 Per aga ni c̱he daa cheej chaochon ile'shi'chi Chioza' cho' wa gonile' cho' nakzi; ḻa' aga bi chon daa gaocho wa daa bi gaocho.
\v 9 Per cho', ḻa'kzi chakbe'icho aga bi zakii lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka' na' ṉezicho aga bi nonan shi yeej gaocho diika' blliagake' lawinka', chiyaḻ' wsak'cho kwenc̱he ki wchix̱cho beena' biṉ' gakcha lo xṉez Chioza' gone' daa chakile' nakan mal.
\v 10 Ḻa' shi ṉezile aga bi zakii lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka' na' cheej chaole gana' choe'la'ogake' ḻegakan, na' ile'i to bish' ljwell-le le', beṉ' biṉ' gakcha lo xṉez Chioza', na' nxoll wc̱hoglallee yeej gawe'n, ḻa'kzi chakile' nakan mal.
\v 11 Na' daa chonle daa ṉezile bi nakan mal, nxoll wḻaale lo xṉez Chioza' bish' ljwell-lena' beena' biṉ' gakcha, beena' ḻekzka' wit Crístona' ni c̱he'.
\v 12 Na' daa chonle ka gon bish' ljwell-lena' to dii na yic̱hjlall'do'ena' bi chiyaḻ' gone', lao Crístona'kzan chx̱iṉj chḻenle.
\v 13 Daan shi daa cheej chaw' gonan ka wx̱iṉj wḻen bish' ljwellaa, naklan wen bichga gaw' belaa, kwenc̱he bi gon' ka wx̱iṉj wḻene'.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 De lsens gon' daa chakid' nakan wen. Nad' nak' postl c̱he X̱ancho Jesucrístona'. Nad' ble'idee, na' le' ba nonḻilall'lene' daa bzajniid' le' xtilleena'.
\v 2 Na' ḻa'kzi zoa beṉ' bi chajḻe'gake' nak' postl c̱he Jesucrístona', le' ṉezile nak' postl c̱he'. Na' daa ba nonḻilall'lene' chli'n kan' nakan.
\p 
\v 3 Na' ki chilli'a xtill' beṉ'ka' na bi nak' dowalj postl:
\v 4 Ṉezile wak iṉabnto' goṉ beṉ' dii yeej gaonto' sheḻ'ka'.
\v 5 Na' ḻekzka' wak ikaanto' to noolə nonḻilallee Crístona' na' wc̱he'nto'ne' gana' gonnto' xshin Chioza', ka chon postlka' sto, na' beṉ'ka' nak beṉ' bish' X̱ancho Crístona', na' ḻekzka' Céfaza'.\f + \fr 9:5 \f*
\v 6 ¿Achakile zeelo Bernabéna' len nad' chiyaḻ' gonnto' llinna' kon ṉi'a na'nto'ki kwenc̱he yeej gaonto'?
\v 7 Aga ga zoa soldad chyixj gax̱t c̱he kwine'. Na' biga zoa beṉ' gaze' yag uvana' na' bi yeeje' daa chbian. Ni biga zoa beṉ' gape' no shib wa no xil' na' bi yeeje' xill'bka' kat' chsie'n.
\v 8 Bi gakile nad'zan nia' ka', ḻa' ḻekzka' na leya' bzej dii Moiséza'.
\v 9 Ḻa' leya' nan: “Bi wllino' yix̱ja' cho'a gooṉka' kat' chlej chshoshjgakb trígona'.” Na' aga toz c̱he gooṉkan' ze Chioza' wṉeyi.
\v 10 San daa zie' wṉeyi c̱hechon wne' ka'. Ḻa' leya' byojan kwenc̱he gaklenan cho'. Ka beena' chwaaṉ gooṉna', na' ka beena' chonshao' trígona', nongake' lez lengake' ikaagake' daa chizi' chilapgake'.\fig Ki chonshao'gake' trigona'.|src="47_HK00096B.TIF" size="COL" ref="1 Corintios 9:10"\fig*
\v 11 Na' shi neto' naknto' ka beṉ' goz daa ba bzajniinto' le' cho'a xtill' Chioza', ¿achakile zi'telan gonnto' iṉabinto' le' shi bi chyalljinto'?
\v 12 Shi beṉ'ka' sto chli' chsedi le' choe'le daa chyallj chc̱hingakile', ¿alechla neto'?
\p Per chonnto' banez bibi chṉabinto' le' kwenc̱he bibi gombeg wzenagle dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona'.
\v 13 Ṉezkzile beṉ'ka' chon llin ḻoo lill xḻatj Chioza' cheej chaogake' daa chjwa' beṉ'ka' lao Chioza'. Na' bx̱ozka' chit bayix̱'ka' lao Chioza' de lsens gaogake' xpel' bayix̱'ka' chitgake'.
\v 14 Na' ka'kzə X̱ancho Crístona' bllie' bia' c̱he beṉ'ka' chyix̱jee dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'na', ḻekzan ibangakile'.
\v 15 Per nad' ni tshii biṉ' iṉabid' le' goṉle dii chyalljid', ni bi chzej' dga kwenc̱he goṉlen. Wenchlan guet' aga ka daa iṉa beṉ' c̱ha' chon' xshin Crístona' daa naxjid'. Ḻa' chibaid' iṉia' bibi chc̱hix̱j' chon' xshine'na'.
\p 
\v 16 Na' nad' bi gak wshalj wshon' daa chyix̱ji'a dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona', ḻa' chonan byen gon' daa none' lall' na'. ¡Na' nyesh'laz gak c̱ha' shi bi wi'a dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'na'!
\v 17 Na' sheḻ'ka' chyix̱ji'an daa goljan ḻoo yic̱hjlall'dawaani, na' chidoḻ' sia' laxj', sheḻ'ka'. Per aga chyix̱ji'an daa goljan ḻoo yic̱hjlall'dawaanin, san zeelo chon' daa ben Crístona' lall' na' gon'.
\v 18 Na' dgan baneza' chizi'a: daa ḻe chibaid' chyix̱ji'a dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona' na' bibi iṉabid' beṉ' wzenague'n, ḻa' bi cheenid' ibanid' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'na', ḻa'kzi wak gon ka', sheḻ'ka'.
\p 
\v 19 Ḻa'kzi kono beṉ' chṉabi'e nad', chon kwin' ka beṉ' ndoo lla yel lao yog'ḻoḻ beṉ' daa choe'lengakee xtill' Crístona', kwenc̱he shanch beṉ'ka' gonḻilall'gake'ne'.
\v 20 Kat' zoa' ladj beṉ' Israelka', beṉ'ka' nak beṉ' wlall c̱ha', na' chsa' c̱ha' ka nsa' c̱hegake' kwenc̱he gonḻilall'gake' Crístona'. Na' chon' daa na leya' bzej dii Moiséza' daa nogake' ḻa'kzi ṉezid' bich chṉabi'an nad'.
\v 21 Na' kat' zoa' ladj beṉ'ka' bi nombia' ley daa bzej dii Moiséza', na' chsa' c̱ha' ka nsa' c̱hegake' kwenc̱he gonḻilall'gake' Crístona'. Per bi iṉacho chzoa' ka'lə daa nllia Chioza' bia', ḻa' chzenag' c̱he leya' daa bzoa Crístona' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'dawaani.
\v 22 Na' kat' zoa' ladj beṉ'ka' chaki dii zan dii bi de lsens gongake', na' chsa' c̱ha' ka nsa' c̱hegake' kwenc̱he wzajni'chgakidee c̱he Crístona'. Ba bsa' c̱ha' ka nsa' c̱he yog'ḻoḻgake' kwenc̱he gon' gan yisla' baḻgake' na' bi kwiayi'gake'.
\v 23 Chon' yog' diiki kwenc̱he wzenag beṉ' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona' na' yizi'lengakee banez c̱heyin.
\p 
\v 24 Ṉezkzile ka nak c̱he beṉ'ka' chxoṉj, zangake' chxoṉjgake', per tochokzen' gone' gan na' ikee daa chidoḻee. Na' ka chon beena' chxoṉj kwenc̱he gone' gan, kan' chiyaḻ' gonle, ḻi gon ka dii le gonle ka cheeni Chioza' kwenc̱he goṉe' daa si'le banez.
\v 25 Beṉ' wyitjka' chsed, chbej yic̱hjgake' daa chzoazi'yaa kwerp c̱he'ka'. Na' chongake' ka' kwenc̱he idoḻ' illongakile' daa yibagakile' xtit shloll na' te c̱heyin. San cho' choncho to dii byen kwenc̱he idoḻ' illonicho to dii biga llia te c̱heyin.
\v 26 Daan, nad' bi chon' ka beena' kon chxoṉj ni bi ṉezile' gan illine', ni bi chon' ka beena' chdiḻ na' bi chzakile' kwalle' beena' chdiḻ-lene'.
\v 27 San chṉabi'a kwin' kwenc̱he chon' daa chiyaḻ' gon' kwenc̱he ki, ka yiyoll wli' wsedid' beṉ' nakan chiyaḻ' gone', nad'lə bi sho'lall'zi Chioza' ka nsa' c̱ha'.
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', bi cheenid' gaḻ-lall'le daa gok c̱he dii x̱ozxto'choka', yog'gake' wloogake' nez xan beja' daa bze Chioza' na' yog'gake' bidegake' lo neza' bsalje' ḻoo nisdo'na'.
\v 2 Na' yog'gake' nakgake' ka beṉ' wchoa nis daa gokgake' dii Moiséza' txen biyajlengake'ne' xan beja' na' daa bidelengake'ne' lo neza' daa byalj ḻoo nisdo'na'.
\v 3 Na' yog'ḻoḻe' wdaogake' toz yeḻ' wao daa be' Chioza' ḻegake'.
\v 4 Na' yog'ḻoḻgake' weejgake' toz nis daa bi'e ḻegake', nisa' daa gol ḻee yaja', yaja' daa zaklebi Crístona', beena' wzoalene' ḻegake'.
\v 5 Ḻa'kzi yog'ḻoḻgake' wxi'gake' banez diika', zangake' bi biyoolallii Chioza' ka bengake', na' witgake' gana' bibi chashj chḻeb.
\p 
\v 6 Na' yog' diika' gok c̱hegake' chzajniin cho' bi chiyaḻ' selall'cho goncho dii mala' ka bengake'.
\v 7 Bi chiyaḻ' we'la'ole diika' non beṉ' lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka' ka ben baḻgake', ḻa' Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Wche'gake' weej wdaogake' na' biyolla' bengake' kon daa nazan c̱he beli chen c̱he'ka'.”
\v 8 Na' bi chiyaḻ' gat'lencho nottez beṉ', ka ben baḻgake', na' daa bengake' ka', shllaz wit shoṉichoa milgake'.
\v 9 Na' bi chiyaḻ' wzoacho Chioza' gone' daa nazan c̱hecho, ka ben baḻgake', na' daa bengake' ka' wdiṉyaa beḻka' ḻegake' na' witgake'.
\v 10 Ni bibi gon iṉazle c̱he Chioza' ka ben baḻgake' na' ni c̱heyin bseḻee anjl c̱he'na' beena' bete' ḻegake'.
\p 
\v 11 Na' yog' diiki gok c̱hegake' nakan to dii chzajnii cho' bi goncho ka bengake', na' lliagakan ḻee Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' kwenc̱he chsi'nin cho' mbancho llaki zeelo.
\v 12 Daan, nottezcho shi chakicho zoac̱hec̱hcho nonḻilall'cho Crístona', chiyaḻ' wsak'cho kwenc̱he bi ibix̱cho goncho dii mala'.
\v 13 Yog' dii malka' chdiḻ chllagle nakgakan ka diika' chdiḻ chllag nottez beṉ'. Na' wak wx̱enilall'le Chioza' gaklene' le', ḻa' ḻen' bi wi'e latj idiḻ illagle daa bi so sakile, san kat' idiḻ illaglen, ḻekzen' gaklene' le' kwenc̱he so sakile yichejle lawinna'.
\p 
\v 14 Daan, le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, bi we'la'ole diika' non beṉ' lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka'.
\v 15 Chshaljlen' le' ba nteile, na' kwinkzle gakbe'ile shi dga chzajniid' le' nakan shḻi.
\v 16 Kat' chisa'lall'cho daa wit Crístona' ni c̱hecho, na' cheejcho lat' wej vinona' na' choe'cho Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken, zejin nakcho Crístona' txen daa blalj xc̱hene'na' ni c̱hecho. Na' kat' chxoxjcho yetxtila' na' chaochon, zejin nakchone' txen daa bzani kwerp c̱he'na' wite' ni c̱hecho.
\v 17 Na' ḻa'kzi nakcho beṉ' zan, toz yetxtilan' chaocho, na' zejin nakcho ka toz kwerp.
\p 
\v 18 Na' ḻi wwia ka chon beṉ' Israelka'. Yog' beṉ'ka' chaogake' xpel' bayix̱'ka' chitgake' lao Chioza' nakgake' toz choe'la'ogake'ne'.
\v 19 Na' bi gakile nia' lwaa lsak' daa non beṉ' chios c̱he'ka' nakgakan dii zakii, ni bi gakile' bel' c̱he bayix̱'ka' chitgake' lawinka' zak'chgakan ka bittezə bel'.
\v 20 San ki zejin daa nia' ka': kat' beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall'gake' Chioza' chitgake' bayix̱'ka' chlliagake'n lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka', dii x̱iw'ka'lan choe'gake'n, na' aga Chiozan'. Na' bi cheenid' we'la'olenle ḻegake' dii x̱iw'ka'.
\v 21 Bi gak yeej gaocho daa cheej chaocho kat' chisa'lall'cho daa wit X̱ancho Crístona', na' ḻekzka' yeej gaotezcho daa cheej chao beṉ'ka' choe'la'o dii x̱iw'ka'.
\v 22 Bi chiyaḻ' wshaacho Chioza', ḻa' aga wzo wzakichone'.
\p 
\v 23 Dez dill', nagake': “Wak goncho bittez dii cheenicho.” Dii ḻikzan, per aga yog' daa gak goncho nakan wen. Ḻa'kzi de latj goncho bittezə, aga yog' daa goncho gaklenan bish' ljwellchoka' gakchachgake' lao Chioza'.
\v 24 Ni tocho bi chiyaḻ' goncho ka gak wen c̱he tozcho, san chiyaḻ' gaklencho beṉ' yoblə kwenc̱he gak wen c̱he'.
\p 
\v 25 Bittezə bel' dii chit'gake' lao yaana' wakə si'len. Na' bi iṉable shi nakan dii blliagake' lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'ka' kwenc̱he bi gakc̱hoplall'le c̱heyin.
\v 26 Ḻa' doxen yell-lioni na' yog'te daa de lawinna' nakan c̱he X̱ancho Chioza'.
\p 
\v 27 Shi to beṉ' bi nonḻilallee Crístona' chaxe' le' lljtaole lille'na', na' cheenile' shajle, ḻi yeej ḻi gao daa goṉe', na' bi iṉabilene' shi nakan dii bllie' lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱he'na' kwenc̱he bi gakc̱hoplall'le c̱heyin.
\v 28 San shi no iṉa le': “Beli nakan dii wllia lao lwaa lsak' chios c̱ha'ka'”, na' bi gaolen ni c̱he beena' wna le' ka'. Ḻa' beena' wna ka' wakte gakile' malan chonle shi gaolen.
\v 29 Bi gakile nia' malan gonle gaolen, san nia' ka' ni c̱he beena' gakile' malan chonle shi gaolen.
\p Ḻa'kzi ṉezid' aga bi nonan gaw' bittezə, bi cheenid' gon' ka sa'lall' beṉ' yoblə nan malan' chon'.
\v 30 Na' shi cho'a Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken c̱heyi daa gaw', ¿berac̱he iṉaz beṉ' malan chon' daa chaw' to dii ba bi'a Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken c̱heyin?
\v 31 Na' bittezə dii chonle, shi cheej chaole wa shi bichlə dii yoblə chonle, chiyaḻ' gonlen ka sho' Chioza' balaaṉ.
\v 32 Bi gonle ka ixop beṉ' yoblə gone' to dii mal, ḻaa nake' beṉ' Israel, ḻaa bi nake' beṉ' Israel, ḻaa nake' beṉ' nakcho txen nonḻilall'cho Chioza'.
\v 33 Ḻi gon ka nad', ḻa' chon' to dii byen toshiizi chon' ka yiyoolallii yog' beṉ'. Aga chon' kwenc̱he to nad'zə gak wen c̱ha', san chon' ka gak wen c̱he beṉ' yoblə kwenc̱he yilagake' bi kwiayi'gake'.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Ḻi wsa' to c̱hele ka nsa' c̱ha', ḻa' nad' nsa' c̱ha' ka bsa' c̱he Crístona'.
\p 
\v 2 Ḻe wen chonle daa toshiizi chjadinile nad' na' ni zejlenle diika' bli' bsedid' le'.
\v 3 Per cheenid' shajniile dga: Chioza' chṉabi'e Crístona', na' Crístona' chṉabi'e yog'ḻoḻ beṉ' byo, na' beṉ' byoka' chṉabia'gake' nool c̱he'ka'.
\v 4 Na' nottezə beṉ' byo shi nkwash' yic̱hje'na' shlak choe'ḻwille' Chioza' wa shlak chyix̱ji'e daa che' Chioza'ne', bi chgwee Crístona' balaaṉ.
\v 5 San shi nottez nool bi wkwash' yic̱hje'na' shlak choe'ḻwille' Chioza' wa shlak chyix̱ji'e daa che' Chioza'ne', na' chṉite' balaaṉ c̱he beṉ' c̱he'na'. Na' shi ka' chone', na' nake' ka to noolə beṉ' nshib ax̱t lo yej.
\v 6 Na' shi to noolə bi wkwash' yic̱hje'na', wenlan wshibteguen' ax̱t lo yej. Na' shi chido'ile' wshiben', chiyaḻ' wkwasheen.
\v 7 Na' beṉ' byona' bi chiyaḻ' wkwash' yic̱hje'na' daa nake' lwaa lsak' Chioza' na' chli'e balaaṉ c̱he'na'. Na' noola' chli'e balaaṉ c̱he beṉ' c̱he'na'.
\v 8 Ḻa' aga kwit ḻee noolan' wlej Chioza' beṉ' byona', san noolan' wleje'ne' kwit ḻee beṉ' byona'.
\v 9 Na' ni bi bx̱ie' beṉ' byona' kwenc̱he gaklene' noola', san bx̱ie' noola' kwenc̱he gaklene' beṉ' byona'.
\v 10 Ni c̱heyi daan, na' ni c̱he anjlka' len ladjchoka', chiyaḻ' wkwash' yic̱hje'ka' kwenc̱he nakbia' chapgake' balaaṉ beṉ' c̱he'ka'.
\v 11 Per cho' nakcho X̱ancho Crístona' txen, ṉezicho noolka' chyalljgakile' cho' beṉ' byo, na' cho' beṉ' byo chyalljicho noolka'.
\v 12 Ḻa' ka nak daa bchej noola' kwit ḻee beṉ' byona', ḻekzka' beṉ' byona', noolan' chzane' ḻe'; per Chiozan' bx̱e bsile' yog'ḻoḻ.
\p 
\v 13 Na' le'zə, ḻi wwiakachi shi nakan wen we'ḻwill noolka' Chioza' gaḻ' yic̱hjzgake'.
\v 14 Kon ka yoolocho choncho, chakbe'icho nakan yeḻ' zto' we'z beṉ' byona' latj igol yish' yic̱hje'na'.
\v 15 San nakan wen we' noola' latj igol yish' yic̱hje'na' na' nakan to balaaṉ c̱he'. Ḻa' Chioza' none'n kwenc̱he wkwasha'n yic̱hje'na'.
\v 16 Na' shi nole bi chazlall'le dga ba wnia', chiyaḻ' iṉezile ka neto' na' ka yog' kwen beṉ'ka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Chioza', toz ka yoolonto' chonnto'.
\p 
\v 17 Na' ka nak dga iṉia' le', bi gak iṉia' ḻe wen chonle. Ḻa' kat' chdop chllagle choe'la'ole Chioza' lwaayin dii nan gaklenan le', chzoazi'yaalan le'.
\v 18 Zigaate cheenid' iṉia' le' daa ba benid' nagake' c̱hele nan kat' chdop chllagle choe'la'ole Chioza' nonzə c̱he c̱hel-le. Na' chajḻi'a dii ḻiljakz ka chonlen.
\v 19 Na' chakljayile chiyaḻ' gakle c̱hop shoṉ kwenlə kwenc̱he wli'lawin nolen chazlalli Chioza' ka chonle.
\v 20 Na' kat' chdop chllagle na' cheej chaolen ljwell-le txen kwenc̱he chisa'lall'le daa wit X̱ancho Jesucrístona', bi chonlen ka bllie' bia'.
\v 21 Ḻa' kat' yeej gaole, bi chbez ljwell-le kwenc̱he yeej gaole txen, san to tole lii cheej chaotele yeḻ' wao c̱heleka'. Na' baḻ-le bibi de gaole na' zi baḻ-le ax̱t chzollile.
\v 22 ¿Abi zoa lill-le ga yeej gaole? ¿Berac̱he chonzile nakzi beṉ'ka' nakcho txen choe'la'ocho Chioza' na' chsi'zle yeḻ' zto' beṉ'ka' bibi de yeej gaogake'? ¿Bitgui iṉiale, lla? ¿Achakile iṉia' le' ḻe wen chonle? Bi iṉia' le' ka', ḻa' aga wenan chonle.
\r (Mt. 26:26-29; Mr. 14:22-25; Lc. 22:14-20)
\p 
\v 23 Dga ba bli' bsedid' le' nakan daa bli' bsedi X̱ancho Jesucrístona' nad'. Lle'na' ben Júda'ne' lo na' beṉ' malka', X̱ancho Jesúza' bex̱ee yetxtila',
\v 24 na' biyoll bi'e Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken, na'ch bxoxje'n na' chi'e: “Dgan kwerp c̱ha'ni daa chzanid' ni c̱hele. Ḻi gox̱' lat' wejan gaolen. Ḻi gon dga kwenc̱he lljadinile nad'.”
\v 25 Na' ḻekzka' biyoll wdaogake' xshe'na', bex̱ee kopa' daa yoll vinona', na' chi'e: “Dga yollə ḻoo kopi zejin x̱chen'na' daa ḻaljə daa gon ka gakḻi dii koba' bc̱heb Chioza' gone'. Ḻi gon dga, na' to to ka yeejlen ḻi lljadini nad'.”
\v 26 Na' to to ka gaole yetxtila' na' yeejle vinona' ax̱t llana' yiyed X̱ancho Crístona' zejin chyix̱je'ile beṉ' ka nak daa wite' ni c̱hecho.
\p 
\v 27 Nottezə beṉ' gawe' yetxtila' wa yeeje' vinona' daa chonan ka lljadinicho X̱anchona', na' bi chape' balaaṉ ka nak daa chone', toz ka nak xtoḻeena' ka c̱he beṉ'ka' betgake' X̱anchona' na' blaljgake' xc̱hene'na'.
\v 28 Daan, to tocho chiyaḻ' yiya yiyilj kwincho kat' zi' gaocho yetxtila' na' kat' zi yeejcho vinona'.
\v 29 Ḻa' Chioza' wsak'zi'e nottez beṉ' konteḻe yeej gawe'n na' bi gone'n ka kwee X̱ancho Crístona' balaaṉ daa bzani kwerp c̱he'na' ni c̱hecho.
\v 30 Daan, zanle bi shao'le wa zoazi'yaale, na' baḻ beṉ'ka' nakle txen ba witgake'.
\v 31 Per shi yiya yiyilj kwincho, X̱ancho Chioza' bi wsak'zi'e cho'.
\v 32 Na' shi chsak'zi'e cho', chone'n kwenc̱he yigooshḻilall'cho na' bi wlliayi'lene' cho' beṉ'ka' bi nonḻilall'gake'ne'.
\p 
\v 33 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', kat' chdop chllagle kwenc̱he yeej gaole, ḻi kwez ljwell-le.
\v 34 Na' shi nole chbiḻ chdonle, chiyaḻ' yeej gaole ḻoo yoo lill-le kwenc̱he bi gonle ka gonan byen tele yeḻ' zak'zi' daa bi chonle wen kat' chdop chllagle. Dech diika' cheenid' wzajniid' le', na' kwaa xṉezin kat' yidwia' le'.
\c 12
\p 
\v 1 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', cheenid' iṉezile c̱he diika' noṉ Espíritu c̱he Chioza' gak gon to tocho.
\p 
\v 2 Ṉezkzile kana' biṉ' gonḻilall'le X̱ancho Jesúza', bentezle txen beṉ'ka' choe'la'o lwaa lsak' chioska' diika' ni bi chak iṉe.
\v 3 Daan, cheenid' iṉezile ni to beṉ' bi iṉe': “Aga bi zakii Jesúza'” shi zoalen Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ḻe'. Na' ḻekzka' ni to beṉ' bi gak iṉe': “Jesúza' nake' X̱ancho” shi bi zoalen Espíritu Santo c̱he Chioza' ḻe'.
\p 
\v 4 Wde wdeli daa choṉ Espíritu c̱he Chioza' to tocho, per ḻekzen' choṉe' yog'tegakan.
\v 5 Wde wdeli nak xshin X̱ancho Crístona' goncho, per toze' ḻen' nak X̱ancho.
\v 6 Na' wde wdeli nak daa none' lall' na'cho gon to tocho, per toz Chiozan' chaklene' cho' kwenc̱he chak chonchon.
\v 7 Chioza' chli'e zoalen Espíritu c̱he'na' cho' daa noṉe' to tocho diika' chak choncho kwenc̱he chaklenan yog'cho.
\v 8 Na' ba bene' kwenc̱he Espíritu c̱he'na' chaklene' baḻcho choe'lencho beṉ' dill' kon yeḻ' sin' c̱he'na', na' zi baḻcho, chone' ka chajniicho daa nak c̱he Chios na' chak chzajniichon beṉ' yoblə.
\v 9 Na' zi baḻcho, chon Espíritu c̱he'na' ka chajḻe'chacho gone' daa iṉabichone'; na' zi baḻcho, chone' ka gak yiyoncho beṉ'.
\v 10 Na' zi baḻcho, chc̱hine' kwenc̱he choncho yeḻ' wak; zi baḻcho, chone' ka chak chyix̱je'cho daa na Chioza' cho'; zi baḻcho, chone' ka chakbe'icho shi dillaa choe' beṉ' dii ḻi nakan c̱he Chioza' wa shi nakan c̱he dii x̱iwaa. Zi baḻcho, chone' ka chak chṉecho wde wdeli dill' dii bi nsedcho; na' zi baḻcho, chone' ka chak chizajniicho bin wna beena' chṉe dillaa.
\v 11 Na' toz Espíritu c̱he Chioza' chgwee xṉezin goncho yog' diika', na' ḻe' chgone' daa gon to tocho.
\p 
\v 12 Na' ka kwerp c̱hechona' nakan toz ḻa'kzi zan diika' ndiḻ nllagan, ka'kzə cho' nonḻilall'cho Crístona' nakchone' toz ḻa'kzi nakcho beṉ' zan.
\v 13 Na' yog'ḻoḻcho cho', ka beṉ' Israel, ka beṉ' griego, ka beṉ' ndoo lla yel chone' xshin beṉ', na' ka beṉ' chon xshinkze', Espíritu c̱he Chioza' ba bene' kwenc̱he nakcho ka toz kwerp. Na' toz ḻen' yo'e ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do' to tocho.
\p 
\v 14 Na' ka nak kwerp c̱hechona', zan diika' ndiḻ nllagan.
\v 15 Na' shi ṉi'achona' iṉan: “Daa bi nak' neena', bi ndiḻ nllag' kwerpa'.” Ḻa'kzi shi iṉan ka', ndiḻ nllagkzan kwerpa'.
\v 16 Na' shi nagchona' iṉan: “Daa bi nak' jalawe'na', bi ndiḻ nllag' kwerpa'.” Ḻa'kzi shi iṉan ka', ndiḻ nllagkzan kwerpa'.
\v 17 Na' sheḻ'ka' doxen kwerp c̱hechona' nakan jalaocho, ¿nakra goncho kwenc̱he yenicho? Na' shi doxen kwerp c̱hechona' nakan nagcho, ¿nakra goncho kwenc̱he iḻa'icho?
\v 18 Na' Chioza' bzoe' to to diika' ndiḻ nllag kwerp c̱hechona' kon gana' chakile' nakan wen soa to ton.
\v 19 Ḻa' sheḻ' toz ka nak yog'te daa ndiḻ nllagan, bi nakan to kwerp sheḻ'ka'.
\v 20 Na' ḻa'kzi zan diika' ndiḻ nllaggakan kwerp c̱hechona', tozkz kwerpan nakan.
\p 
\v 21 Na' jalaochoka' bi gak ye'gakan na'choka': “Bi chyalljid' le'.” Ni bi gak ye' yic̱hjchona' ṉi'achoka': “Bi chyalljid' le'.”
\v 22 Na' diika' ndiḻ nllag kwerp c̱hechona' daa chakicho bi nakan wal, ḻeləgakannan' llialote.
\v 23 Na' diika' ndiḻ nllag kwerp c̱hechona' daa chakicho bitek bi zaka'n, ḻeləgakannan' chapshiicho. Na' diika' bi cheenicho ile'i beṉ' chkwashi'chon xachona'.
\v 24 Na' diika' ndiḻ nllag kwerp c̱hechona' na' bi chonan ka yiyii yido'icho ile'i beṉ' ḻegakan, bi chonan byen wkwash'chon. Na' ka' ben Chioza' kwerp c̱hechona' kwenc̱he nkwash'cho diika' chonan ka yiyii yido'icho ile'i beṉ' ḻegakan.
\v 25 Na' yog' diika' ndiḻ nllag kwerpa' chaklen ljwellin daa nakgakan toz.
\v 26 Daan shi gayi kwerp c̱hechona' chey chla, doxen kwerpa' bi shao'. Na' shi gayi kwerp c̱hechona' chonichon wen, doxenan chibayi.
\p 
\v 27 Na' le' nakle ka kwerp c̱he Crístona' daa naklene' toz, na' to tole nakle ka tkwen wej kwerp c̱he'na'.
\v 28 Na' ladjchona', cho' chdop chllagcho choe'la'ocho Crístona', Chioza' llialote bzoe' neto' naknto' postl, na'ch bzoe' beṉ' chyix̱ji'e daa chi'ene', na' de wyoṉi bzoe' beṉ' wli' wsedile' beṉ' cho'a xtilleena'. Na'ch bzoe' beṉ' wli'e yeḻ' wak c̱he'na', na' beṉ' yiyone' beṉ', na' beṉ' gaklen bish' ljwellchoka', na' beṉ' chgoo xṉezin c̱he xshine'na', na' beṉ' chṉe wde wdeli dill' dii bi nsede'.
\v 29 Ṉezicho aga yog'cho nakcho postl. Aga yog'cho chak c̱hix̱je'cho daa na Chioza' cho'. Aga yog'cho chak wli' wsedicho cho'a xtilleena'. Na' aga yog'cho chak goncho yeḻ' wak.
\v 30 Aga yog'cho chak yiyoncho beṉ'. Aga yog'cho chak iṉecho wde wdeli dill' dii bi nsedcho. Na' aga yog'cho chak yizajniicho bi zeji dill'ka'.
\v 31 Na' le', ḻi selall' gaklen Espíritu c̱he Chioza' le' kwenc̱he gak gonle diika' zak'chi.
\p Na' ṉaa wsedid' le' to dii llialaotech.
\c 13
\p 
\v 1 Shi nad' chak' wde wdeli dill' dii chṉe beṉ' yell-lioni na' ax̱t len xtill' anjlka' chak', per bi chakid' beṉ', aga bi zjanayin chak' diika', na' nak' ka to dii nak de ya dii chon daṉe wa ka platiy dii chon sshag.
\v 2 Na' ḻa'kzi shi chak c̱hix̱ji'a daa na Chioza' nad', na' ṉezid' yog'ḻoḻ daa nak c̱he Chioza' ax̱t daa kochnoṉ' iṉezi, na' ḻa'kzi shi ḻe chajḻi'a c̱he Chioza' ax̱t chon' ka illa' xishna' yaaka', shi bi chakid' beṉ', aga bi zjanayin chak gon' diika'.
\v 3 Na' ḻa'kzi shi wi'a beṉ' yesh'do'ka' yog' dii de c̱ha', wa izanid' kwerp c̱ha'ni kwenc̱he wzeygake'n, shi bi chakid' beṉ', aga bi gaklenan nad' lao Chioza'.
\p 
\v 4 Shi chakicho beṉ', gapcho yeḻ' chxenlall' c̱hegake', gonicho ḻegake' wen, bi gakxe'icho ḻegake', bi wshalj wshoncho lawe'ka', bi gakcho beṉ' cha'sibə,
\v 5 bi gonichogake' zban, bi c̱hiljcho daa nak to banez c̱hezcho, bi gakcho zgaaḻ zyil, ni bi koolall'cho.
\v 6 Ni bi yibaicho kat' no chon mal, san yibaicho kat' no chon wen.
\v 7 Shi chakicho beṉ', bi goncho dii choo dii xen bittez dii chonile' cho', na' bi sa'lall'cho mal c̱he', san toshiizi goncho lez gone' wen, na' so sakicho bittezə.
\p 
\v 8 Yeḻ' chakina' aga wiyoll widon. San ka nak daa chyix̱jee beṉ' daa che' Chioza'ne', na' daa iṉe beṉ' wde wdeli dill' dii bi nsede', wllin lla bich iyalljan, na' ni bich bi iyalljicho iṉezicho.
\v 9 Ḻa' lat'chga daa ṉezicho ṉaa, na' lat'chga daa na Chioza' cho' kwenc̱he chyix̱je'ichon beṉ',
\v 10 per kat' illin lla Chioza' gone' ka gombia'chone' kwasḻoḻ, na' te c̱heyi diika' chzajniin cho' lat' wej ṉaa.
\p 
\v 11 Kana' nak' bi'do', bshalj' ḻega bi'do', ben' pensar ka bi'do', na' wyajniid' ḻega bi'do'. Per ka bgol' bich bsa' c̱ha' ka c̱he bi'do'.
\v 12 Ka'kzan chak c̱hecho kon daa nak c̱he Chioza' ṉaa. Nakcho ka to beṉ' chwia to lo wan dii bi nḻa'yeṉ'. Per wllin lla kat' ile'yeṉ'ichone' ka chle'i cho'alao ljwellcho. Biṉ' gombia'yeṉ'cho Chioza' ṉaa, per wllin lla kat' gombia'chone' kwasḻoḻ ka nombi'e cho'.
\v 13 Na' ṉaa diiki shoṉə nakgakan dii llialote goncho: gonḻilall'cho Chioza', gonchone' lez, na' gapcho yeḻ' chakina'. Na' daa llialote lawi diiki shoṉ, ḻennan' yeḻ' chakina'.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Ḻi gon byen gakile' bish' ljwell-leka' na' ḻekzka' ḻi selall' goṉ Espíritu c̱he Chioza' le' to dii gak gonle, na' daa llialoch selall'le gone' ka gak c̱hix̱je'le daa iṉa Chioza' le'.
\v 2 Ḻa' beena' chṉe dill' daa kono chajnii, Chiozan' chshaljlene', aga beṉ' yell-lionin. Ḻa' Espíritu c̱he Chiozan' chone' ka cho'e dill' daa kono chajnii.
\v 3 San beena' chyix̱jee daa che' Chioza' ḻe', chone' ka gakchach beṉ' lao Chioza', na' chtipe' lall'gake' na' chiyonxenlallee ḻegake'.
\v 4 Beena' chṉe dill' daa kono chajnii, to ḻe'zen' chaklenan, san beena' chyix̱jee daa che' Chioza'ne' chaklene' yog' beṉ'ka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona' kwenc̱he gakchagake' lo xṉeze'na'.
\p 
\v 5 Nad' cheenid' sheḻ'ka' yog'ḻoḻ-le gak iṉele dill'ka' daa kono chajnii, per wibachid' sheḻ'ka' gak c̱hix̱je'le daa iṉa Chioza' le'. Ḻa' dii zak'chi daa chyix̱jee beṉ' daa na Chioza' aga ka daa iṉie' dill' daa kono chajnii, ḻete shi yizajniile' beṉ'ka' bin zeji dill'ka' chṉie' kwenc̱he gakchachgake' lao Chioza'.
\v 6 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', shi nad' yidwia' le' na' iṉia' dill' daa kono chajnii, bi gaklenan le'. Ḻete waklenan le' shi wzajniid' le' to dii ba bli' bsedi Chioza' nad', wa to dii chiyaḻ' iṉezile c̱he', wa c̱hix̱je'id' le' bi iṉe' nad', wa wli' wsedid' le' cho'a xtilleena'.
\p 
\v 7 Kachaka' blleja' wa no dii llia kwerd c̱heyin, kono shajnii bin chkwellgake' shi bi chllaa shiinka'.
\v 8 Na' kat' chak to wdiḻ, shi beena' chkwell clarínna' bi wkwelle'n kwasḻoḻ, aga no idop illag kwenc̱he shajgake' lo wdiḻa'.
\v 9 Na' ka'kzan chak c̱hele, shi iṉele dill' daa bi chajnii beṉ', nakra gone' shajniile' bin nale. Na' bibi zakii dill'ka' chṉele shi ṉaa.
\v 10 Ṉezicho zan kwen xtill' beṉ' de yell-lioni na' to togakan chajnii beṉ'ka' chṉegake'n.
\v 11 Na' shi bi chajniid' dillaa we'len to beṉ' nad', nak' ka beṉ' zit' par ḻe', na' ḻekzka' ḻe' nake' ka beṉ' zit' par nad'.
\v 12 Na' daa ba chzelall'le goṉ Espíritu c̱he Chioza' daa gak gonle, ḻi gon ka dii le iṉable daa gaklenan bish' ljwell-leka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona' kwenc̱he gakchachgake' lawe'na'.
\p 
\v 13 Daan, beena' chṉe dill' daa kono chajnii, chiyaḻ' iṉabile' Chioza' gaklene'ne' kwenc̱he gak yizajniile' beṉ' bin zeji dillaa chṉie'.
\v 14 Ḻa' shi chshaljlen' Chioza' dill' daa bi chajniid', yic̱hjlall'dawaani ṉezin chshaljlen' Chioza', per bi chajniid' bin chepee.
\v 15 ¿Beran chiyaḻ' gon', lla? Chiyaḻ' we'ḻwill' Chioza' kon dill' daa na Espíritu c̱he'na', na' ḻekzka' we'ḻwillee kon dill' daa chajniid'. Na' ḻekzka' chiyaḻ' goḻ' kon dill' daa na Espíritu c̱he'na', na' goḻ' kon dill' daa chajniid'.
\v 16 Ḻa' shi we'la'ole Chioza' kon dill' daa kono chajnii, ḻa'kzi nakan c̱he Espíritu c̱he Chioza', beṉ'ka' yengakile' dill'ka' chṉele aga gongake' le' txen we'le yeḻ' chox̱ken Chioza' ḻa' bi chajni'gakile' bin nale.
\v 17 Ḻa'kzi choe'le Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken do yic̱hj do lall'le, bi chaklenan beṉ' yoblə daa bi chajni'gakile' bin nale.
\v 18 Cho'a Chioza' yeḻ' chox̱ken daa chṉech' dill' daa kono chajnii aga ka yog'tele.
\v 19 Per kat' ndop nllagcho choe'la'ocho Chioza' txen, wenchlan iṉia' gay'zə dill' daa chajniicho kwenc̱he wzajniid' beṉ' yoblə, aga ka daa iṉia' ga shi mil dill' daa kono chajnii.
\p 
\v 20 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', bi gonzle pensar ka bi'do' biṉ' shajnii, san ḻi gon pensar ka beṉ' golə, beṉ' ba chajnii. Per ka nak c̱he dii mala', ḻi gak ka to bi'do' biṉ' sho' yic̱hjin dii mala'.
\v 21 Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Wc̱hin' beṉ' zit', beṉ' chṉe dill' yoblə, kwenc̱he wzajniid' beṉ' Israelki, per ni ka' bi wzenaggake' c̱ha', na X̱ancho Chioza'.”
\v 22 Daan, kat' chṉecho dill' daa kono chajnii chonan kwenc̱he beṉ'ka' bi chonḻilall'gake' Chioza' gakbe'gakile' zoalene' cho' per bibi chzajniin cho' ba nonḻilall'chone'. San daa c̱hix̱je'cho daa na Chioza' cho', chaklenan cho' ba nonḻilall'chone' per bi chaklenan beṉ'ka' bi chonḻilall'gake'ne'.
\v 23 Na' kat'ka' ndop nllagle choe'la'ole Crístona', shi yog'zle choe'le dill' daa kono chajnii, na' sho' beṉ' bi chajniile' bin chonle wa beṉ' biṉ' gonḻilall' Crístona', wak gakile' bi nza'n c̱helenan'.
\v 24 San shi yog'le chyix̱je'le daa na Chioza' le', na' sho' to beṉ' biṉ' gonḻilall' Crístona' wa to beṉ' bi chajnii bin chonle, na' yiyakbe'ile' nake' beṉ' saaxya na' yiyaj yilenile' dii malka' chone' ka yenile' dill'ka' chyix̱je'le.
\v 25 Na'ch gonan ka wli'lawi daa yoo ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'ena', na' wc̱hek' xibe' we'lawee Chioza', na' gakbe'ile' dii ḻicha Chioza' zoalene' le'.
\p 
\v 26 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', kat' chdop chllagle de latj kwenc̱he baḻ-le goḻ-le dii koon Chioza' balaaṉ, na' zi baḻ-le wli' wsedile, zi baḻ-le c̱hix̱je'le daa na Chioza' le', na' zi' baḻ-le iṉele dill' daa kono chajnii, na' zi baḻ-le yizajniile dillaa kono chajnii. Yog' diiki chiyaḻ' wc̱hinlen kwenc̱he gaklenan soac̱hec̱hle lo xṉez Chioza'.
\v 27 Na' kat' iṉele dill' daa kono chajnii, c̱hopzle wa shoṉzle iṉelen, na' yizoayile iṉele, na' chiyaḻ' soa to beṉ' yizajniile' bin wnale.
\v 28 Na' shi kono zoa beṉ' chak yizajniile' bin iṉale, bi chiyaḻ' iṉelen gana' ndop nllagle choe'la'ole Crístona', san wak iṉelenlen Chioza' de ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'lena'zə.
\v 29 Na' ḻekzka' c̱hop shoṉzlen c̱hix̱je'le daa na Chioza' le', na' yizoayile iṉele. Na' beṉ'ka' chzenag, chiyaḻ' wzenagyeṉ'gake' shi dii ḻi nakan daa na Chioza'.
\v 30 Shi shlak to beṉ' chyix̱ji'e dillaa daa che' Chioza'ne', na' iṉe Chioza' sto beṉ' chi'e ladjlena', chiyaḻ' kwez beena' chṉe kwenc̱he c̱hix̱jee beena' sto daa che' Chioza'ne'.
\v 31 To tole yizoayile c̱hix̱je'le daa na Chioza' kwenc̱he yog'le shajni'chile diika' na Chioza' na' wtipch lall'le.
\v 32 Na' beena' chyix̱jee daa che' Chioza'ne' chiyaḻ' iṉabia' kwine' kwenc̱he wi'e latj iṉe beṉ' yoblə, shi ṉaa.
\v 33 Ḻa' Chioza' cheenile' gonle xochi yog' daa chonle kat' choe'la'olene' na' bi gonle kon daa nazan c̱hele.
\p Ka yoolo beṉ'ka' choe'la'o Crístona' yog'te gana' chdop chllaggake',
\v 34 noolka' chiyaḻ' soagake' llizə gana' chdop chllagle, ḻa' bi de lsens iṉegake'. San chiyaḻ' wc̱hek' yic̱hj wc̱hek' laogake' lao beṉ'ka' chṉabia' ḻegake', kon ka na ley daa bzej dii Moiséza'.
\v 35 Na' shi de daa cheengakile' iṉezgakile', chiyaḻ' iṉabgakile' beṉ' c̱he'ka' ḻoo yoo lillgake', ḻa' bi nakan wen iṉegake' kat' ndop nllagle.
\p 
\v 36 Bi gakile zigaate ladjlenan' golj wxe cho'a xtill' Chioza', ni bi gakile le'chgan ba bleblen.
\v 37 Shi nole chakile nakle beṉ' chyix̱jee daa na Chioza', wa chakile Espíritu c̱he Chioza' chzajniile' le', chiyaḻ' gakbe'ile dga chzej' le' nakan dii chon X̱ancho Crístona' mandad.
\v 38 Na' shi no bi chzenag c̱heyi dga chzej' le', ḻekzka' kono wzenag c̱he'.
\p 
\v 39 Na' le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, ḻi selall' gak c̱hix̱jeele daa na Chioza' le', na' bi wllonle iṉe beṉ' dill' daa kono chajnii.
\v 40 Per bittezə dii gonle, ḻi gonan kon ka chiyaḻi na' xochi ḻi gonan.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', cheenid' yisaa lall'le dill' wen dill' koba' wdix̱je'id' le' daa ba bleble na' zoac̱hec̱hle chajḻe'le c̱heyin.
\v 2 Ḻa' ḻennan' yislan le' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'le shi toshiizi soac̱hec̱hle shajḻe'le daa ba wdix̱je'id' le'. Na' shi bi soac̱hec̱hle toshiizi aga bi zjanayin daa nale ba wyajḻe'le c̱heyin.
\p 
\v 3 Bli' bsedid' le' dga bzajnii Chioza' nad' daa nakan dii llialote: nan Crístona' wite' ni c̱hecho daa nakcho beṉ' saaxya, kon ka na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza'.
\v 4 Na' bkwash'gake'ne' na' biyoṉ lla bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', kon ka na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza'.
\v 5 Na' bli'lawe' Céfaza',\f + \fr 15:5 \ft Céfas: kan' le Pédrona' de dill' arameo, daa gok xtill' Jesúza'.\f* na'tech bli'lawe' postlka' sto.
\v 6 Na'tech bli'lawe' wdeli gay' guiyoa beṉ' bish'choka' na' beṉ' zanchoka' nonḻilall'gake'ne'. Na' zan beṉ'ka' ni mban lla ṉaanlla, na' baḻgake' ba wit.
\v 7 Na'tech bli'lawe' Jacóbona', na' wdena' bli'lawe' yog' postlka'.
\p 
\v 8 Na' zeeloteyi bli'lawe' nad', ḻa'kzi nak' beṉ' bibi zakii.
\v 9 Nad' nak' ḻiizelozi beṉ' bibi zakii ladj beṉ'ka' wlej Crístona' gongake' xshine'na', na' bi chidoḻaa iṉa beṉ' nad' “postl”, daa bsak'zi'a beṉ'ka' chonḻilall'gake'ne'.
\v 10 Per daa nak Chioza' beṉ' chiyesh'lallii, wleje' nad' wi'a xtill' Crístona'. Na' daa biyeshlallile' nad' bi gokdadzan, ḻa' ba bench' xshine'na' aga ka yog' postlka' sto. Per aga tobia'lozan' bena'n, san ḻen' ba goklene' nad' kwenc̱he bena'n.
\v 11 Na' ḻa'kzi nad' wa postlka' sto choe'lennto' beṉ' xtilleena', toz ka dill' choe'nto', na' ḻennan' ba wyajḻe'le.
\p 
\v 12 Na' daa chyix̱je'nto' biban Crístona' ladj beṉ' wetka', ¿berac̱he nazə baḻ-le bi yiban beṉ' wetka'?
\v 13 Ḻa' sheḻ' bi yiban beṉ' wetka', ḻekzka' aga biban Crístona' sheḻ'ka'.
\v 14 Na' sheḻ' Crístona' bi bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', aga bi zakii daa chyix̱je'nto' cho'a xtilleena', ni aga bi zakii daa nonḻilall'lene', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 15 Na' sheḻ' bi yiban beṉ' wetka', aga dill' ḻi c̱he Chiozan' be'lennto' le' daa wnanto' Chioza' bisbane' Crístona' ladj beṉ' wetka', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 16 Ḻa' sheḻ' bi yiban beṉ' wetka', aga biban Crístona', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 17 Na' sheḻ' Crístona' bi bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', aga bi zjanayin nonḻilall'lene', na' ni napkzle doḻ' c̱he saaxya c̱heleka', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 18 Na' sheḻ' nakan ka', beṉ'ka' benḻilall'gake' Crístona' na' ba witgake', wlliayi'chokzgaken', sheḻ'ka'.
\v 19 Na' sheḻ' to lo yell-lionizan noncho lez gaklen Crístona' cho', nyesh'lazch nakan c̱hecho aga ka c̱he yog' beṉ' yoblə, sheḻ'ka'.
\p 
\v 20 Per dii ḻi Crístona' bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', na' daa bibane' neche' ladj beṉ' wetka' zaklebile' dii necha' chizi' chilap beṉ'.
\v 21 Daa bx̱iṉj bḻen toz beṉ', wyoo yeḻ' wita' yell-lioni, na' ḻekzka' toz beṉ' bx̱ie' daa yiban beṉ' wetka'.
\v 22 Ka chet yog' beṉ' ni c̱he daa bx̱iṉj bḻen dii Adánna', ka'kzan yiban beena' nak Crístona' txen.
\v 23 Per to to beṉ' yibane' ladj beṉ' wetka' kat' illin llana' nllia Chioza' bia' yibangake'. Zigaate Crístona' bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', na' kat' yiyed Crístona', ḻekzka' yiban yog' beṉ'ka' nak lall' nee.
\v 24 Na' te c̱he yell-lioni kat'ka' wlliayi' Crístona' yog'ḻoḻ yeḻ' wak na' yeḻ' wṉabia' yoblə, na' yiyo'e yeḻ' wṉabia' c̱he'na' X̱acho Chioza'.
\v 25 Ḻa' Crístonan' chiyaḻ' iṉabi'e ax̱t ki yiyoll yido wzoe' xṉi'ena' yog' beṉ'ka' chakzi' chakzbani ḻe' na' yog' dii x̱iw'ka'.
\v 26 Na' yiyollin, wlliayee yeḻ' wita'.
\v 27 Cho'a xtill' Chioza' nan Chioza' bzoe' xṉi'a Crístona' yog'ḻoḻte dii de. Na' daa nan yog'ḻoḻte zoa xṉi'a Crístona', aga len Chiozan' zoe' xṉi'ena', ḻa' ḻen' bzoe' xṉi'a Crístona' yog'ḻoḻte dii de.
\v 28 Na' kat'ka' yog'ḻoḻte dii de ba zoan xṉi'a Crístona', na'ch kwin Crístona', beena' nak Xiiṉ Chioza', wzex̱j yic̱hje' lao Chioza', beena' bzoa yog'te dii de xṉi'ena'. Na'ch gakbia' nan Chioza' nake' ḻiizelozi beṉ' zakii lao yog'ḻoḻte dii de.
\p 
\v 29 Na' chiznia' sto, ¿bera zejin daa chchoa baḻ beṉ' nisa' lwaa beṉ' wetka'? Shi chakgakile' bi yiban beṉ' wetka', ¿berac̱he chchoazgake' nisa' lwaagake'?
\p 
\v 30 Na' sheḻ'ka' bi yiban beṉ' wetka' ¿berac̱he zoaznto' dii nxoll gak dii gak c̱hento' do lla do yel?
\v 31 Dii ḻi, le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', yog' lla zoa' dii nxoll guet'. Na' ḻekzka' dii ḻicha ḻe chiba chizakid' c̱hele daa ba nonḻilall'le X̱ancho Jesucrístona'.
\v 32 Yell Éfesona' wdiḻ-len' beṉ'ka' nak ka ba zṉia nlleb, ¿beratgui gon' gan wdiḻ-lengakee sheḻ'ka' bi yiban beṉ' wetka'? Gonchokljacho ka dillaa de daa na: “Yeej gaotezcho ḻa' wetcho wx̱e willj.”
\p 
\v 33 Bi we'le latj no siye' le'. Ḻa' dill' de, nan: “Shi goncho txen beṉ' malka' na' solo goncho ka chongake'.”
\v 34 Ḻi yiyeeṉi kwasḻoḻ na' bich gonle dii mala', ḻa' baḻ-le ni bi nombia'le Chioza'. Nia' le' ka' kwenc̱he yido'latile.
\p 
\v 35 Wnalja baḻ-le: “¿Nakra gak yiban beṉ' wetka'? Na' ¿Nakra yiyak kwerp c̱he'ka'?”
\v 36 Shi ka' nale, nakle ka beṉ' bi nteyi. Kat' chazcho biṉna', bi chila' yagdo'na' shi bi chbiayi' biṉna'.
\v 37 Kat' chazcho, aga yagdo'nan' chazcho, san biṉ c̱heyinnan' chazcho, na' chila' yagdo'na'. Na' kan' chak c̱he bittezə dii chazcho, shi no trigo wa bichlə.
\v 38 Na' Chioza' chgwee xṉez xḻatjin chakan ka cheenile', na' to to biṉ chak xyaguinna' kon ka chiyaḻ' gak c̱he to ton.
\v 39 Aga toz ka nak kwerpka'. Nlla'lə nak kwerp c̱he beṉec̱ha' len c̱he bayix̱'ka'. Na' nlla'lə nak c̱he baka' chzo xan yabana' na' c̱he beḻka' lle' ḻoo nisa'.
\v 40 Ḻekzka' nak c̱heyi diika' lle' xan yabana' na' diika' chle'icho lo yell-lioni. Nlla'lə yeḻ' xochi c̱heyi diika' chle'icho xan yabana' len yeḻ' xochi c̱heyi diiki chle'icho lo yell-lioni.
\v 41 Nlla'lə yeḻ' chey cheeni' c̱he wbilla' len c̱he beo'do'na' na' len c̱he beljka'. Na' ladj beljdo'ka' nlla'lə nak yeḻ' chey cheeni' c̱he to togakan.
\v 42 Na' ka'kzan gak c̱he beṉ'ka' yiban ladj beṉ' wetka'. Kwerpa' daa chgash' ḻoo bana' nakan dii gooll' iteb, san kwerp daa yiyas kat' yibancho ladj beṉ' wetka' bi nakan dii gooll' iteb.
\v 43 Kwerpa' daa chgash' ḻoo bana' nakan dii bichbi zakii, san daa yiyas ladj beṉ' wetka' gakan to dii zakii nlleb. Kwerpa' daa chgash' ḻoo bana' nak bḻan'zan, san daa yiyas ladj beṉ' wetka' gakc̱hec̱han.
\v 44 Kwerpa' daa chgash' ḻoo bana' nakan de beli chenzə dii chon llin yell-lioni, san kwerp daa yiyas ladj beṉ' wetka' gakan to dii kob daa goṉ Chioza'. Na' daa ṉezicho kwerp c̱hechoni nakan de beli chenzə, ḻekzka' chiyaḻ' iṉezicho wat' to kwerp kob c̱hecho daa goṉ Chioza'.
\p 
\v 45 Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' nan: “Adánna', beena' gok beṉ' nech, goke' to beṉ' yaa beṉ' ban.” Na' ḻekzka' Crístona' goke' beṉ' yell-lio, per ḻe' choṉe' yeḻ' mban zejḻi kaṉi.
\v 46 Zigaate chbanlencho kwerp de beli chenni, na'techlan ibanlencho dii koba' daa goṉ Chioza'.
\v 47 Beṉ' necha' ben Chioza' de bishte yo, goke' beṉ' yell-lio. Na' beṉ' wchopina', beena' nak X̱ancho, ḻen' wzee yabana'.
\v 48 Kwerp c̱hechona' nakan ka kwerp c̱he beṉ' necha' bx̱e bsil Chioza' de bishte yona'. Na' ka nak kwerp c̱he Crístona', beena' zoa yabana' ṉaa, ka'kzan yiyak kwerp c̱hechona' kwenc̱he lljazoacho yabana'.
\v 49 Ṉaa nakcho ka beena' ben Chioza' de bishte yo, na' wllin lla yiyakcho ka Crístona', beena' zoa yabana'.
\p 
\v 50 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', cheenid' iṉia' le': Aga wak yillinlencho kwerp de beli chenni gana' zoa Chioza' chṉabi'e. Na' kwerpi dga gooll' iteb bi gak gonan txen kwerp daa bi gooll' iteb.
\v 51 Ni iṉia' le' to dii kono wṉezi: aga yog'cho guetcho, per yog'cho yiyakcho nlla'lə.
\v 52 Tokonganzi, to ka chshod' chx̱a'z jalaochoki, kat' kwell trompet c̱he Chioza', yiyakcho nlla'lə. Ḻa' ka kwell trompeta', beṉ' wetka' yibangake' kon to kwerp dii bi gooll' iteb. Na' cho' ni mbancho, ḻekzka' yilla' kwerp c̱hechoki.
\v 53 Ḻa' kwerp c̱hechoni dga gooll' iteb, yiyakan to dii bi gooll' iteb. Na' beli chen c̱hechoni dga ile'i yeḻ' wita', yiyakan to dii bichga guet.
\v 54 Kat'ka' kwerp c̱hechoni dga gooll' iteb ba biyakan to dii bi gooll' iteb, na' beli chen c̱hechoni dga ile'i yeḻ' wita' ba biyakan to dii bichga guet, na' gak ka na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' daa na: “X̱anchona' ba bene' gan bsol bṉite' yeḻ' wita' toshiizi.”
\v 55 Na' ḻekzka' nan: “Yeḻ' wit, li' chsi chc̱hogo' yeḻ' mban c̱he beṉ', ¿gaṉ yeḻ' wak c̱ho'na' ṉaa?”
\v 56 Daa bi choncho diika' bllia Chioza' bia' goncho chli'n nakcho beṉ' saaxya, na' daa nakcho beṉ' saaxya, yeḻ' wita' napan yeḻ' wak kwenc̱he wsol wṉitan cho'.
\v 57 Per chox̱ken Chioza' bseḻee X̱ancho Jesucrístona' ni c̱hecho kwenc̱he bi saki yeḻ' wita' si' ikaan cho' zejḻi kaṉi.
\p 
\v 58 Daan, le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, ḻi soac̱hec̱h lo xṉez Chioza' toshiizi. Na' zizikli ḻi gon xshin X̱ancho Jesucrístona', ḻa' ṉezkzile xshine'na' aga nakan to llin dii chondadzle.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 Na' ka nak mech daa wtople daa we'le beṉ'ka' nak lall' na' Chioza', ḻi gon ka ben' mandad gon beṉ'ka' chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona' to to yell daa llia gana' mbani Galáciana'.
\v 2 Yog' lla nech c̱he xmanka', to tole chiyaḻ' kwejle lat' wej daa benle gan lo xmanna' na' kooshao'len kwenc̱he bibi wtople kat' yid'.
\v 3 Na' kat' yid' gana' zoale, wseḻaa beṉ'ka' kwejle lljwa'gake' Jerusalénna' mecha' daa btople, na' wgox̱'gakee yish daa wzej' kwenc̱he beṉ' Jerusalénka' wlebgake' ḻegake'.
\v 4 Na' shi chonan byen shaa, na' sha'len' ḻegake'.
\p 
\v 5 Chonan byen tia' gana' mbani Macedóniana', na' ka tia', yidwia' le'.
\v 6 Na' waklja yigaaṉlen' le' shloll wa soalen' le' ax̱t ka yiyollch te dii zaga'. Na' kat' yigwaa nez yiyaa gan yoblə wak gaklenle nad' goṉle daa iyallj ic̱hinid'.
\v 7 Aga shlollzan cheenid' yidwia' le', san non lez yigaaṉlen' le' ssha, shi X̱ancho Chioza' wi'e latj.
\v 8 Na' ṉaa cheenid' yigaaṉa' yell Éfesoni ax̱t ka gaḻ' lṉi Pentecostéza',
\v 9 ḻa' beṉ' zan lle' ni, beṉ' cheeni wzenag xtill' Jesucrístona', ḻa'kzi beṉ' zan chllaagake' daa choe'len' beṉ' xtilleena'.
\p 
\v 10 Na' shi ba za' Timotewa' gana' zoale, ḻi gonile wen, ḻa' ḻekzka' lene' chone' xshin X̱ancho Jesucrístona' ka chon' nad'.
\v 11 Na' ni tole bi gonilene' nakzi, san ḻi gaklene' yigwee neza' mbalaz kwenc̱he yidwie' nad', ḻa' chbeztia'ne' kon beṉ' bish'choka' sto.
\p 
\v 12 Na' ka nak beṉ' bish'cho Apólozi, ḻe got'yoidee yidlene' beṉ' bish'choki yidwiagake' le', per bi goonile' yide' ṉaa, per widkze' kat' gat' latj c̱he'na'.
\p 
\v 13 Ḻi se kwas na' ḻi soac̱hec̱h gonḻilall'chle Crístona'. Ḻi gakcha lo xṉeze'na' na' bi illeble.
\v 14 Na' bittezə dii gonle, ḻi gonan ḻega beṉ' chaki ljwellin.
\p 
\v 15 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', ṉezile beṉ'ka' lle' lill Estéfanazi gokgake' beṉ' nech beṉ' benḻilall'gake' Crístona' gana' mbani Acáyana', na' zoatekzgake' chli' chsedgakile' beṉ'ka' nak lall' na' Chioza'.
\v 16 Chat'yoid' le', ḻi wzenaggach c̱he beṉ'ka' chon ka ḻegake', na' ḻi wzenag c̱he yog' beṉ'ka' chaklen chongake' xshin Chioza'.
\v 17 Ḻe chibaid' daa ba bid Estéfanazi len Fortunátoni na' Acaíconi gani zoa', ḻa' daa zoalengake' nad' ni, bich chakyeshid' daa biṉ' gak yidwia' le'.
\v 18 Ba biyoṉgake' nad' to yeḻ' chxenlall' ka daa choṉgake' le'. Ka beṉ'ki na' ka beṉ'ka' chon ka ḻegake', chidoḻ'gake' gaple ḻegake' balaaṉ.
\p 
\v 19 Beṉ'ki chdop chllag choe'la'ogake' Crístona' to to yell gani mbani Ásiani chwapgake' le' chiox. Na' Aquílani len Priscílani, len beṉ'ka' chdop chllag lille'ka' chwapgake' le' chiox do yic̱hj do lall'gake' daa nakle X̱ancho Crístona' txen.
\v 20 Na' yog' beṉ' bish'choka' lle' ni chwapgake' le' chiox. Na' ḻi wwap ljwell-le chiox ḻega beṉ' chaki ljwellin daa nakle lall' na' Chioza'.
\p 
\v 21 Nad', Pablo, kwin' chzej'\f + \fr 16:21 \ft Kwin' chzej': Páblona' bc̱hine' beṉ' bzeje' dillaa bi'e, per kwine' bzeje' to c̱hop cho'a dill' gana' chiyoll yisha' kwenc̱he gokbe'gakile' ḻen' bseḻeen.\f* gani chwap' le' chiox.
\p 
\v 22 Nottezə beṉ' bi chakile' X̱ancho Jesucrístona', wsak'zi'shga Chioza'ne'. ¡Bidagach X̱an'!
\p 
\v 23 X̱ancho Jesucrístona' soalenshgue' le' na' gaklenshgue' le'.
\v 24 Ḻe chakid' yog'le daa nakcho Jesucrístona' txen.
